e:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong m\u1ed9t chia s\u1ebb m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam L\u00ea C\u00f4ng Vinh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 ra c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00f3a gi\u1ea3i s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Malaysia.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 16.5pt;\"><span id=\"ctl00_m_contentBody_sp_title\" class=\"sp_title\" style=\"font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; font-family: arial, verdana, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: start;\">C\u00f4ng Vinh m\u00e1ch n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ec3 \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u1ea1 Malaysia</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, verdana, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; text-align: start;\">&nbsp;<br>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mot nam duoi thoi Quyen chu tich Le Cong Vinh, CLB TP.HCM da co nhieu thay doi tich cuc. Anh: Tung Le/Zing.vn\" title=\"M\u1ed9t n\u0103m d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Quy\u1ec1n ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch L\u00ea C\u00f4ng Vinh, CLB TP.HCM \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u thay \u0111\u1ed5i t\u00edch c\u1ef1c. \u1ea2nh: T\u00f9ng L\u00ea/Zing.vn\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/3/cong-vinh-mach-nuoc-de-dt-viet-nam-ha-malaysia.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>C\u00f4ng Vinh tin t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd h\u1ea1 Malaysia. \u1ea2nh: Zing.vn</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Malaysia s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u chung k\u1ebft s\u1edbm t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng A <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/aff-cup-c334-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">AFF Cup 2018</span>. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n l\u1eabn l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean Malaysia ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. V\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o L\u00ea C\u00f4ng Vinh \u0111\u00e3 m\u00e1ch n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo &lsquo;h\u00f3a gi\u1ea3i&rsquo; \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Malaysia c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh, th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1t&rdquo;, C\u00f4ng Vinh t\u00e2m s\u1ef1. &ldquo;N\u1ebfu \u0111\u00e1 v\u1edbi Malaysia, ch\u00fang ta c\u1ea7n kho\u00e1 ch\u1eb7t 2 c\u00e1nh c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 bi\u00ean ph\u1ea3i v\u1edbi g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t tr\u1ebb Akhyar Rashid r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Malaysia l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 h\u1ecd ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o c\u1ef1u binh Talaha&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ec9 ra c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3 v\u1edbi Malaysia, c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o L\u00ea C\u00f4ng Vinh c\u0169ng \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo. Danh th\u1ee7 x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh: &ldquo;T\u00f4i tin ch\u1eafc n\u1ebfu ch\u01a1i \u0111\u00fang phong \u0111\u1ed9, \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Vi\u1ec7t Nam ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Malaysia tr\u00ean s\u00e2n M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y hai n\u0103m, C\u00f4ng Vinh v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1eebng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Malaysia \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-0 nh\u1edd pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Tr\u1ecdng Ho\u00e0ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00f3, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 H\u1eefu Th\u1eafng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch khi b\u1ecb Indonesia lo\u1ea1i \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 16.5pt; text-align: justify;\"><em><u>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n</u></em><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/aff-cup-2018/anh-duc-lot-top-5-cau-thu-an-tuong-nhat-aff-cup-2018-334-202174.html\">Tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng HLV Park Hang Seo l\u1ecdt top 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t AFF Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/aff-cup-2018/nguoi-thai-coi-dt-viet-nam-la-moi-nguy-hiem-lon-nhat-o-aff-cup-2018-334-202170.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i coi \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 m\u1ed1i nguy hi\u1ec3m l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t \u1edf AFF Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/day-thong-ke-dang-mung-cho-dt-viet-nam-truoc-tran-gap-malaysia-292-202164.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng m\u1eebng cho \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Malaysia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thuyen-truong-malaysia-khang-dinh-se-choi-tan-cong-truoc-viet-nam-168-202162.html\">Thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Malaysia kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/tan-binh-dt-viet-nam-co-ben-do-moi-voi-muc-lot-tay-khung-168-202183.html\">T\u00e2n binh \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c l\u00f3t tay c\u1ef1c kh\u1ee7ng</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:18.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&#10;&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5599","checkdouble":"202193"},{"date":"18:00 13/11","title":"\u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ea5u Malaysia: \u0110\u00e1 ph\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u hay ru ng\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/11/13/dt-viet-nam-dau-malaysia-da-phu-dau-hay-ru-ngu-doi-thu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y n\u1eefa, tr\u1eadn Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Malaysia s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra. V\u00e0 li\u1ec7u HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m?</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 16.5pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Th\u1ea7y Park v\u00e0 b\u00e0i to\u00e1n h\u1ea1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi M\u00e3<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 16/11 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u chung k\u1ebft s\u1edbm t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng A gi\u1eefa \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Malaysia s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra tr\u00ean SV\u0110 qu\u1ed1c gia M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 song c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p thi \u0111\u1ea5u l\u01a1 l\u00e0, khi m\u00e0 \u0110T Malaysia lu\u00f4n nguy hi\u1ec3m v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng v\u00e0i l\u1ea7n khi\u1ebfn ch\u00fang ta &lsquo;\u00f4m h\u1eadn&rsquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">G\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, t\u1ea1i AFF Cup 2014, ng\u01b0\u1eddi M\u00e3 t\u1eebng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 4-2 ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Toshiya Miura khi \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Malaysia \u0110\u00e1 ph\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u hay ru ng\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Malaysia \u0110\u00e1 ph\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u hay ru ng\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/2/DT-Viet-Nam-vs-Malaysia-Da-phu-dau-hay-ru-ngu-doi-thu-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1eebng nh\u1eadn tr\u00e1i \u0111\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Malaysia t\u1ea1i AFF Cup n\u0103m 2014.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i thi\u00ean v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i tranh ch\u1ea5p, \u0110T Malaysia lu\u00f4n lu\u00f4n t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e2u h\u1ecfi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t ra l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 li\u1ec7u ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ph\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u1edd l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 hay \u0111\u00e1 c\u00f2 c\u01b0a, ru ng\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tung ra nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f2n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh?<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u, \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n th\u00f4i, c\u1ee9 x\u1ebfp m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p L\u00e0o, \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0m ch\u1ee7 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean c\u00f3 hai v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 lo ng\u1ea1i l\u00e0 li\u1ec7u tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa v\u1edbi Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, Quang H\u1ea3i c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng &lsquo;m\u00e1y qu\u00e9t&rsquo; gi\u1eefa s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Malaysia v\u00e0 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 t\u1ec9nh t\u00e1o \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba c\u00e1c \u0111\u00f2n t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng 'h\u1ed3i m\u00e3 th\u01b0\u01a1ng' c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/video-ban-thang-viet-nam-24-malaysia-ban-ket-aff-cup-2014-325-100664.html\">Video b\u00e0n th\u1eafng: Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2-4 Malaysia (B\u00e1n k\u1ebft AFF Cup 2014)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\r\n<p style=\"font-weight: normal;\">D\u0129 nhi\u00ean khi tri\u1ec3n khai m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u00e2ng cao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng s\u1ebd ph\u00e1t sinh nh\u1eefng b\u1ea5t c\u1eadp n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a FLC Thanh H\u00f3a c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o: <em>&quot;\u0110\u00e1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 con dao hai l\u01b0\u1ee1i. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u00ec ch\u00fang ta khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd kh\u00f3 l\u00ean b\u00f3ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c sai l\u1ea7m n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng h\u1ecfng. Nh\u01b0ng m\u1eb7t kh\u00e1c, khi &quot;qu\u00e2y&quot; \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1eeb s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd th\u00ec ph\u00eda sau l\u01b0ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd l\u1ed9 ra nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng l\u1edbn v\u00e0 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u01a1n&quot;.<br>\r\n</em></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Park Hang Seo\" title=\"HLV Park Hang Seo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/11/11/hlv-le-thuy-hai-lo-ngai-cho-dt-viet-nam-truoc-tran-gap-malaysia.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Park Hang Seo ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111ang \u0111au \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea5u Malaysia</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"font-weight: normal;\">Do v\u1eady n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea9n th\u1eadn, \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 b\u1edfi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. Malaysia t\u1eebng cho th\u1ea5y \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u1edf Asiad n\u00ean h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y v\u1edbi \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-weight: normal;\">Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, n\u1ebfu \u0111\u00e1 &lsquo;c\u00f2 c\u01b0a&rsquo; ch\u1edd c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd an to\u00e0n h\u01a1n nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi nhau t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u00e0m xuy\u00ean th\u1ee7ng m\u00e0nh l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-weight: normal;\">S\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u1eabn \u0111ang l\u00e0 n\u1ed7i tr\u0103n tr\u1edf c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park t\u1ea1i <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/aff-cup-c334-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">AFF Cup 2018</span>. \u1ede tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p L\u00e0o, t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam&nbsp;ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 50/50. V\u00ec v\u1eady, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p phung ph\u00ed s\u1ed1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u00edt \u1ecfi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\u0110\u00e2u l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ea5u Malaysia?<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 an to\u00e0n khi ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Malaysia thay v\u00ec c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ph\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi L\u00e0o.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n, \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m v\u1eabn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 1. \u1ede v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 l\u1ebd B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng s\u1ebd v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh t\u00e1i ph\u00e1t ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Khi \u1ea5y su\u1ea5t thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a anh s\u1ebd thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Qu\u1ebf Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh DTVN\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0110TVN\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/11/13/lineup.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn&nbsp;Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Malaysia&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 b\u1ed9 ba Duy M\u1ea1nh, \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea3i s\u1ebd l\u00e0 hai h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 bi\u00ean V\u0103n H\u1eadu v\u00e0 Tr\u1ecdng Ho\u00e0ng. \u1ede tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p v\u1edbi Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, \u0111\u1ea9y Quang H\u1ea3i l\u00ean cao \u0111\u00e1 nh\u01b0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u00e1nh h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 Anh \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eafm. Su\u1ea5t c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft ho\u1eb7c C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Malaysia l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng d\u1ed3i d\u00e0o th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 qu\u00e2n b\u00e0i chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y Park s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00f9ng V\u0103n To\u00e0n ho\u1eb7c Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c trong hi\u1ec7p 2 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn. Khi \u0111\u00f3, h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/doi-tuyen-viet-nam-c292-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">\u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam </span>s\u1ebd th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nhanh nh\u1eb9n, c\u00f3 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Malaysia s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra l\u00fac 19h30 ng\u00e0y 16/11 tr\u00ean SV\u0110 M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh. Bongda24h s\u1ebd c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn, k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c n\u00e0y. Mong b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u00f3n xem.</p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/11/8/Lao-0-3-Viet-Nam.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em><u>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:</u></em></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/day-thong-ke-dang-mung-cho-dt-viet-nam-truoc-tran-gap-malaysia-292-202164.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/11/8/day-thong-ke-dang-mung-cho-dt-viet-nam-truoc-tran-gap-malaysia.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/day-thong-ke-dang-mung-cho-dt-viet-nam-truoc-tran-gap-malaysia-292-202164.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng m\u1eebng cho \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Malaysia</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng v\u1edbi Malaysia v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 16/11 t\u1edbi, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1m y\u00ean t\u00e2m khi bi\u1ebft th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y: \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i SV\u0110 M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cong-vinh-mach-nuoc-de-dt-viet-nam-ha-malaysia-168-202193.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/3/cong-vinh-mach-nuoc-de-dt-viet-nam-ha-malaysia.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cong-vinh-mach-nuoc-de-dt-viet-nam-ha-malaysia-168-202193.html\">C\u00f4ng Vinh m\u00e1ch n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ec3 \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u1ea1 Malaysia</span><br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t chia s\u1ebb m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam L\u00ea C\u00f4ng Vinh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 ra c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00f3a gi\u1ea3i s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Malaysia.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thuyen-truong-malaysia-khang-dinh-se-choi-tan-cong-truoc-viet-nam-168-202162.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/11/13/thuyen-truong-malaysia-khang-dinh-se-choi-tan-cong-truoc-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thuyen-truong-malaysia-khang-dinh-se-choi-tan-cong-truoc-viet-nam-168-202162.html\">Thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Malaysia kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nS\u1ee9c n\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn ng\u00e0y 16/11 t\u1edbi \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean r\u1ea5t cao, khi HLV Malaysia tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 3 v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 16.5pt; text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5598","checkdouble":"202195"},{"date":"17:50 13/11","title":"4 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 khi\u1ebfn Bayern Munich kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/11/13/4-cau-thu-khien-bayern-munich-khoi-dau-te-hai.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Bayern Munich kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19, h\u1ecd \u0111ang x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 5 \u1edf Bundesliga v\u00e0 k\u00e9m \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng Dortmund t\u1edbi 7 \u0111i\u1ec3m. C\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua danh s\u00e1ch 4 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i.\r\n</h2><h2>Manuel Neuer</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nManuel Neuer t\u1eebng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c. Tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n, Neuer kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"4 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 khi\u1ebfn Bayern Munich kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i \u1edf m\u00f9a 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"4 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 khi\u1ebfn Bayern Munich kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i \u1edf m\u00f9a 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/11/13/4-cau-thu-khien-Bayern-Munich-khoi-dau-te-hai-o-mua-201819-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Manuel Neuer</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 32 tu\u1ed5i ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i \u1edf World Cup 2018 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c, giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a n\u00e0y anh c\u0169ng g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t tr\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Bayern Munich. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1, ch\u1ecdn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed hay ra v\u00e0o c\u1ee7a Neuer \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1.&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn thua 2-3 c\u1ee7a Bayern tr\u01b0\u1edbc Dortmund m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1986 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. Ch\u00ednh phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Manuel Neuer l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Bayern Munich kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i \u1edf m\u00f9a 2018/19.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a 2016/17, Neuer ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi 0.5 b\u00e0n/tr\u1eadn, m\u00f9a n\u00e0y anh \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn t\u1edbi 14 b\u00e0n thua sau 11 tr\u1eadn (1,27 b\u00e0n/tr\u1eadn). C\u0169ng \u1edf m\u00f9a 2016/17, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1986 c\u00f3 1,9 l\u1ea7n c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1/tr\u1eadn, nh\u01b0ng m\u00f9a n\u00e0y con s\u1ed1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 1,1 l\u1ea7n/tr\u1eadn. Trong s\u1ed1 18 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ra s\u00e2n \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 5 tr\u1eadn \u1edf Bundesliga m\u00f9a n\u00e0y, Manuel Neuer \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 17 v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n c\u1ee9u thua/tr\u1eadn.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nFranck ribery</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nFranck Ribery \u0111ang c\u00f3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ee9 11 g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Bayern Munich, trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m qua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c. Tuy nhi\u00ean, m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1983 \u0111ang g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Franck Ribery gop dau giay trong ca 2 ban thang cua Bayern truoc Sevilla\" title=\"Franck Ribery g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y trong c\u1ea3 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Bayern tr\u01b0\u1edbc Sevilla\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/4/Nhung-diem-nhan-sau-tran-dau-Sevilla-vs-Bayern-Munich---Tu-ket-C1-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Franck Ribery</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 ra s\u00e2n 14 l\u1ea7n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 961 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u, nh\u01b0ng anh ch\u01b0a g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0o. \u1ede tu\u1ed5i 35, Ribery \u0111ang t\u1ecf ra h\u1ee5t h\u01a1i trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111ua t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o hay d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a anh c\u0169ng suy gi\u1ea3m \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, trung b\u00ecnh Ribery t\u1ea1o ra 2.5 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i/90 ph\u00fat cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf Bundesliga, th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 1.6/90 ph\u00fat. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u0169ng gi\u1ea3m t\u1eeb 3.7 l\u1ea7n/90 ph\u00fat xu\u1ed1ng c\u00f2n 1.6 l\u1ea7n/90 ph\u00fat.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u00f9 s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u0103ng l\u00ean (2.2 l\u1ea7n/90 ph\u00fat \u1edf m\u00f9a n\u00e0y so v\u1edbi 1.5 \u1edf m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc) nh\u01b0ng Ribery v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0o sau 9 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf Bundesliga. \u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u00f4ng tin cho r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 35 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi t\u00e2n HLV Kovac. Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Bayern, Uli Hoeness, \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea3i t\u1ed5 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u00e0o m\u00f9a H\u00e8 n\u0103m t\u1edbi, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Ribery s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nMats Hummels</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, Mats Hummels ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c. Tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Bayern Munich, anh ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. Trong tr\u1eadn thua 2-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Dortmund, Hummels li\u00ean t\u1ee5c m\u1eafc l\u1ed7i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 Marco Reus v\u00e0 Paco Alcacer ghi b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mats Hummels\" title=\"Mats Hummels\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/11/13/hum.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mats Hummels</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, Hummels \u0111\u00e3 m\u1eafc 2 l\u1ed7i ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n thua, nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a &ldquo;H\u00f9m x\u00e1m&rdquo;. Ch\u00ednh vi\u1ec7c c\u1ef1u sao Dortmund kh\u00f4ng ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn khung th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Neuer li\u00ean t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng b\u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea c\u1ee7a Hummels \u0111\u1ec1u suy gi\u1ea3m r\u00f5 r\u1ec7t so v\u1edbi m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 1.6 l\u1ea7n c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1/90 ph\u00fat \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, th\u1ea5p con con s\u1ed1 2.3 l\u1ea7n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18. T\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng (1.3 l\u1ea7n/90 ph\u00fat \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y) c\u0169ng suy gi\u1ea3m \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 (m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00e0 2.1 l\u1ea7n/90 ph\u00fat).</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nThomas Muller</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Thomas Muller ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, anh c\u00f3 8 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 14 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o \u1edf Bundesliga. Tuy nhi\u00ean, giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989 \u0111ang ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c ra s\u00e2n 14 l\u1ea7n \u1edf Bundesliga v\u00e0 Champions League nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 ghi 2 b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thomas Muller\" title=\"Thomas Muller\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/11/13/miller.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Thomas Muller</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, trong 739 ph\u00fat g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng ghi b\u00e0n c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o, l\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 anh g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Bayern \u0111\u00e3 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y h\u01a1n 2 th\u00e1ng (01/09).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nThomas Muller c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Kovac v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh.&nbsp;M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 29 tu\u1ed5i d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m 1.9 l\u1ea7n/90 ph\u00fat, m\u00f9a n\u00e0y th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 l\u00e0 1.7. S\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169ng gi\u1ea3m t\u1eeb 2.7 l\u1ea7n/90 ph\u00fat xu\u1ed1ng 1.7.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMuller c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng \u00edt nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/bayern-munich-1567.html\" target=\"_blank\"><em><u>Bayern Munich</u></em></span> \u1edf Bundesliga m\u00f9a n\u00e0y. Trung b\u00ecnh anh ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng 45 l\u1ea7n/90 ph\u00fat, ch\u1ec9 h\u01a1n duy nh\u1ea5t Robert Lewandowski (32).&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5597","checkdouble":"202197"},{"date":"10:21 13/11","title":"G\u00f3c Barca: \u0110\u1eebng th\u1ea5y tr\u0103ng v\u1eb1ng v\u1eb7c m\u00e0 t\u01b0\u1edfng tr\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 s\u00e1ng!","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/11/12/goc-barca-dung-thay-trang-vang-vac-ma-tuong-troi-da-sang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>4 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua, th\u1eafng h\u00f2a thua \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 song c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m chung: Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Barca kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t ch\u00fat n\u00e0o. Sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ho\u00e0nh tr\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real Madrid, d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Ernesto Valverde \u0111\u00e3 r\u01a1i v\u00e0o \u1ea3o t\u01b0\u1edfng n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>C\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 t\u01b0 t\u01b0\u1edfng</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTam qu\u1ed1c di\u1ec5n ngh\u0129a k\u1ec3 r\u1eb1ng v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y gi\u1eefa th\u00e1ng 11, T\u00e0o Th\u00e1o m\u1edf ti\u1ec7c r\u01b0\u1ee3u h\u1ed9i h\u1ecdp c\u00f9ng binh t\u01b0\u1edbng tr\u00ean thuy\u1ec1n. Tr\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed1i nh\u01b0ng m\u1eb7t tr\u0103ng v\u01b0\u01a1n cao tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh n\u00fai ph\u00eda \u0110\u00f4ng v\u00e0 s\u00e1ng v\u1eb1ng v\u1eb7c nh\u01b0 ban ng\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110ang vui c\u01b0\u1eddi b\u00e0n chuy\u1ec7n th\u00f4n t\u00ednh c\u00e1c th\u1ebf l\u1ef1c ch\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ed1i, b\u1ed7ng Th\u00e1o th\u1ea5y \u0111\u00e0n qu\u1ea1 nh\u00e1o nh\u00e1c bay l\u01b0\u1ee3n, k\u00eau h\u00e9t tr\u00ean tr\u1eddi, b\u00e8n h\u1ecfi: &ldquo;<em>L\u0169 qu\u1ea1 l\u00e0m sao l\u1ea1i k\u00eau gi\u1eefa \u0111\u00eam th\u1ebf n\u00e0y?</em>&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea3 h\u1eefu th\u01b0a: &ldquo;<em>Qu\u1ea1 th\u1ea5y tr\u0103ng s\u00e1ng v\u1eb1ng v\u1eb7c, t\u01b0\u1edfng tr\u1eddi s\u00e1ng n\u00ean s\u1edbm ra kh\u1ecfi t\u1ed5 bay v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Nam.</em>&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Barca \u0110\u1eebng th\u1ea5y tr\u0103ng t\u01b0\u1edfng tr\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 s\u00e1ng! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Barca \u0110\u1eebng th\u1ea5y tr\u0103ng t\u01b0\u1edfng tr\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 s\u00e1ng! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/10/31/Phong-do-cua-Barca-Dung-thay-trang-tuong-troi-da-sang!-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Valverde \u0111ang \u1ea3o t\u01b0\u1edfng kh\u00f4ng kh\u00e1c Th\u00e0o Th\u00e1o n\u0103m x\u01b0a</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nChuy\u1ec7n sau \u0111\u00f3 ai c\u0169ng r\u00f5. Xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng \u1ea3o t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i h\u1ebft th\u1ea3y, T\u00e0o Th\u00e1o th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i trong tr\u1eadn X\u00edch B\u00edch \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i th\u1ebf ch\u00e2n v\u1ea1c, chia 3 thi\u00ean h\u1ea1 h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Barcelona c\u1ee7a Ernesto Valverde d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 c\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u00e2m v\u00e0o tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i ch\u1ee7 quan kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp</strong> gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u01b0a. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ho\u00e0nh tr\u00e1ng 5-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real Madrid gi\u00fap h\u1ecd ch\u00ecm trong vui s\u01b0\u1edbng, nh\u01b0ng \u0111i k\u00e8m v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 m\u00e3n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1c th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean Barca l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c qu\u00ean \u0111i m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3. H\u1ecd c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u00fd r\u1eb1ng Real khi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e2m v\u00e0o kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin \u0111i xu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e1y. Barca c\u0169ng qu\u00ean lu\u00f4n r\u1eb1ng khi \u0111ang d\u1eabn 2-1, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian 15 ph\u00fat b\u1ecb Real l\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1edbt v\u00e0 n\u1ebfu c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Luka Modric kh\u00f4ng tr\u00fang c\u1ed9t d\u1ecdc m\u00e0 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a, t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Rafinha vs Modric o tran Real vs Barca\" title=\"Rafinha vs Modric o tran Real vs Barca\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/10/29/Lopetegui-roi-Real-Madrid-Tam-biet-nguoi-dan-ong-bat-hanh!-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf El Clasico l\u00e0 li\u1ec1u thu\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9c cho h\u1ecd</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i sau chi\u1ebfn c\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3, <u>phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Barca tr\u1edf n\u00ean ph\u1eadp ph\u00f9, tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng</u> v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u00fa b\u1ee9t \u0111i m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd. \u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia ph\u1ea3i ch\u1edd t\u1edbi ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd m\u1edbi ghi b\u00e0n duy nh\u1ea5t, v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u1ed9i h\u1ea1ng 3 Cultural Leonesa 1-0 t\u1ea1i c\u00fap Nh\u00e0 vua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nK\u1ebf \u0111\u1ebfn, <u>th\u1ea7n may m\u1eafn ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh c\u00f9ng Barca</u> \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd c\u00f3 2 b\u00e0n ch\u1ec9 trong v\u00f2ng 3 ph\u00fat (87 t\u1edbi 90) qua \u0111\u00f3 th\u1eafng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng \u00e1p ch\u00f3t Rayo Vallecano t\u1ea1i La Liga. T\u1ea1i Champions League, 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Inter Milan kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/messi-tro-lai-va-barca-tham-bai-vi-dau-nen-noi-180-202051.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/11/12/messi-tro-lai-va-barca-tham-bai-vi-dau-nen-noi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/messi-tro-lai-va-barca-tham-bai-vi-dau-nen-noi-180-202051.html\">Messi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 Barca th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i: V\u00ec \u0111\u00e2u n\u00ean n\u1ed7i?</span><br>\r\n<span>Barcelona ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n Lionel Messi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ai ng\u1edd h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i thua th\u1ea3m Real Betis 3-4 ngay t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. D\u01b0 \u00e2m Barca 3-4 Betis ch\u1ec9 ra nh\u1eefng...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/ket-qua-barca-vs-betis-la-liga-11112018-180-202020.html\" target=\"_blank\">Barca th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 3-4 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real Betis</span> ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a h\u01a1n 8 v\u1ea1n kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Camp Nou. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 n\u00f3i l\u00ean r\u1eb1ng tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111ang r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1, c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01a1n thu\u1ea7n n\u1eb1m \u1edf chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2>Qu\u00e1 ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o Messi</h2>\r\n<br>\r\nLionel Messi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 Barca th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real Betis, m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ngh\u1ecbch l\u00fd nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt. V\u1eabn theo lu\u1ed3ng quan \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00ean, d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 <em>s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina c\u00e0ng khi\u1ebfn cho s\u1ef1 ch\u1ee7 quan</em> c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia <em>t\u0103ng th\u00eam m\u1ed9t b\u1eadc</em>.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Messi co cu dup truoc Betis\" title=\"Messi co cu dup truoc Betis\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/11/12/Messi-co-cu-dup-truoc-Betis.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Messi l\u1eadp c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap tr\u01b0\u1edbc Betis ng\u00e0y tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Barca \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1 quen v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c giao b\u00f3ng cho Messi v\u00e0 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i nh\u1eefng ph\u00e9p m\u00e0u t\u1eeb anh. <strong>Bongda24h.vn </strong>c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00ednh c\u00e1ch v\u00e0 th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Messi, nh\u01b0ng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng thi\u00ean b\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a s\u1ed1 10, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay c\u1ea3 khi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 trong t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/tevez-che-messi-luoi-tap-hon-ronaldo-184-196774.html\" target=\"_blank\">\u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 Carlos Tevez ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9</span>, Messi v\u1eabn \u1edf m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. D\u1ea7n d\u00e0, d\u00e0n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Barca (v\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ed1ng c\u1ea5p trong v\u00e0i n\u0103m qua) c\u00e0ng ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c h\u01a1n v\u00e0o ch\u00e2n s\u00fat s\u1ed1 1 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed CLB.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/quan-diem-tevez-nhan-xet-ve-messi-va-ronaldo-180-196925.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/9/14/quan-diem-tevez-nhan-xet-ve-messi-va-ronaldo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/quan-diem-tevez-nhan-xet-ve-messi-va-ronaldo-180-196925.html\">Quan \u0111i\u1ec3m: Tevez n\u00f3i \u0111\u00fang, Messi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ch\u00e0ng l\u01b0\u1eddi!</span><br>\r\n<span>Carlos Tevez nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 Lionel Messi v\u00e0 Cristiano Ronaldo. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eebng t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n, thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng c\u1ea3 hai si\u00eau sao n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 h\u00e9 m\u1edf m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc Betis cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n qua, Messi l\u1eadp m\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u00e3y c\u00e1nh tay tr\u1eadn v\u1edbi Sevilla ng\u00e0y 20/10. C\u1ed9ng g\u1ed9p 2 tr\u1eadn k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean l\u1ea1i, Barca th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1edbi 6 b\u00e0n (th\u1eafng 4-2 v\u00e0 thua 3-4). T\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 7 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Messi, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a anh h\u00f2a 3, thua 2, nh\u1eadn 13 b\u00e0n thua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y l\u00e0 ng\u1eabu nhi\u00ean? Kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1! <strong>C\u00f3 Messi tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, 10 th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Barca c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n \u1ef7 l\u1ea1i</strong>. H\u1ecd tin r\u1eb1ng d\u00f9 c\u00f3 l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi bao nhi\u00eau ch\u0103ng n\u1eefa, v\u1eabn c\u00f3 Messi b\u00f9 \u0111\u1eafp l\u1ea1i b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Nh\u01b0ng s\u1ee9c ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 h\u1ea1n, Leo kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00fac n\u00e0o c\u0169ng s\u1eafm vai &ldquo;Ch\u00faa c\u1ee9u th\u1ebf&rdquo;.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Messi nhin Barca that bai\" title=\"Messi nhin Barca that bai\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/11/12/goc-barca-dung-thay-trang-vang-vac-ma-tuong-troi-da-sang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nh\u01b0ng s\u1ed1 10 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e0nh nh\u00ecn Blaugrana th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd: Th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i 3-4 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Betis c\u0169ng l\u00e0 <em>tr\u1eadn thua \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Barca khi Messi ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1eeb 2 b\u00e0n tr\u1edf l\u00ean t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1edbi nay</em>. N\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y ch\u1ee9ng minh m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/ernesto-valverde-phat-bieu-sau-tran-barca-34-betis-180-202054.html\" target=\"_blank\">h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Blaugrana ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng xu\u1ed1ng c\u1ea5p</span> v\u00e0 h\u1ecd ch\u1eb3ng bu\u1ed3n s\u1eeda sang l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Valverde \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-4-2 v\u1edbi 9 th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean tr\u1eeb Messi v\u00e0 ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 Luis Suarez \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i tham gia ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean. Trong \u0111\u00f3, vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 gi\u00e0u c\u01a1 b\u1eafp l\u00e0 Paulinho kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua. Sang m\u00f9a 2018/19 n\u00e0y, &ldquo;tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng&rdquo; c\u1ee7a Valverde \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Trung Qu\u1ed1c h\u00e1i ra ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i cho \u00f4ng khu trung tuy\u1ebfn m\u1ecfng manh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pique va Lenglet\" title=\"Pique va Lenglet\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/11/6/Barca-cheo-keo-mot-loat-ong-lao-Chua-oi,-ho-khon-kho-den-vay-u-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>H\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c t\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Barca</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ee9c \u00e9p c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 v\u00e0 l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o, c\u1ef1u thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Athletic Bilbao bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i thay \u0111\u1ed5i chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt theo chi\u1ec1u h\u01b0\u1edbng c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn h\u01a1n. S\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-3-3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n, \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea9y cao h\u01a1n v\u00e0 c\u1ed9ng th\u00eam th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 khinh \u0111\u1ecbch nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i, phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Barca tr\u1edf n\u00ean v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ph\u1eadp ph\u00f9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u00ednh ra, <em>Barca hi\u1ec7n s\u1edf h\u1eefu h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t trong v\u00f2ng 20 n\u0103m qua</em>. 10 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua t\u1ea1i La Liga, h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi, \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1998 th\u1eddi Louis van Gaal t\u1edbi nay m\u1edbi l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i. 12 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u00e3 qua c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou nh\u1eadn t\u1edbi 18 b\u00e0n thua, trung b\u00ecnh 1.5 b\u00e0n/ tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 5 \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 con s\u1ed1 nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi ph\u00f2ng tuy\u1ebfn t\u1ec7 c\u1ee1 \u0111\u00f3, Barca li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 v\u1ed7 ng\u1ef1c t\u1ef1 tin s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh c\u00e1c danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn? H\u00e3y \u0111\u1eebng l\u00e0 l\u0169 qu\u1ea1 th\u1ea5y tr\u0103ng v\u1eb1ng v\u1eb7c m\u00e0 t\u01b0\u1edfng tr\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 s\u00e1ng!<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem l\u1ea1i video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Barca 3-4 Betis (V\u00f2ng 12 La Liga 2018/19):<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/11/12/001943-Barca-3-4-Betis.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ea1nh H\u00f9ng (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5596","checkdouble":"202156"},{"date":"10:48 13/11","title":"\"Bom x\u1ecbt\" Barca nh\u1eadn c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o t\u1eeb Deschamps","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/11/13/dembele-nhan-canh-bao-tu-deschamps.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Deschamps cho r\u1eb1ng Ousmane Dembele c\u1ea7n c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng th\u00f3i quen khi l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh th\u00ec may ra m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ee9u v\u00e3n s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p \u1edf Barca.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ousmane Dembele \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Barca \u1edf tr\u1eadn thua s\u1ed1c 3-4 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real Betis ngay t\u1ea1i Camp Nou cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTruy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u01b0a tin Barca kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng khi Dembele th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o r\u1eb1ng anh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ecfe \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 N\u0103m. C\u0169ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u tin \u0111\u1ed3n cho r\u1eb1ng Dembele \u0111\u00e3 vi ph\u1ea1m lu\u1eadt l\u1ec7 \u1edf CLB v\u00e0 b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Deschamps c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Dembele v\u1ec1 th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Deschamps c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Dembele v\u1ec1 th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/11/13/dembele-nhan-canh-bao-tu-deschamps.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>HLV\u00a0Deschamps c\u00f4ng khai ch\u1ea5n ch\u1ec9nh Dembele</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 \u0111ang ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt t\u1ea1i Barca nh\u01b0ng Dembele v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Deschamps g\u1ecdi l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u1ec3 tham d\u1ef1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Nations League v\u1edbi H\u00e0 Lan v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 S\u00e1u v\u00e0 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi Uruguay 4 ng\u00e0y sau \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Deschamps cho bi\u1ebft vi\u1ec7c Dembele \u0111\u1ebfn mu\u1ed9n trong c\u00e1c bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng. V\u00e0 \u00f4ng c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 tr\u1ebb c\u1ea7n thay \u0111\u1ed5i ngay nh\u1eefng th\u00f3i quen l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c x\u1ea5u n\u00e0y n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i ch\u01b0a n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n Barca v\u00ec t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n can thi\u1ec7p v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng chuy\u1ec7n \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. Dembele \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 quen v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c t\u1edbi mu\u1ed9n trong c\u00e1c bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp. V\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00fd do c\u1ee7a Dembele l\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ng\u01b0\u1eddi duy nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ebfn mu\u1ed9n\u201d, HLV Deschamps chia s\u1ebb trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadp trung l\u1eafng nghe h\u01a1n n\u1eefa. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ee9 trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 d\u00f9 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1eddi c\u00f2n tr\u1ebb. Nh\u01b0ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 kh\u00e1c ngo\u00e0i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. Dembele c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i hi\u1ec3u \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00e0ng s\u1edbm c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Ousmane Dembele:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/hlv-valverde-noi-gi-truoc-nghi-an-vui-dap-bom-xit-barca-180-201949.html\">HLV Valverde n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc nghi \u00e1n v\u00f9i d\u1eadp \u201cbom x\u1ecbt\u201d Barca?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/valverde-khen-ngoi-dembele-sau-tran-thang-vallecano-180-201331.html\">Valverde khen ng\u1ee3i Dembele sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Vallecano</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-san-sang-thanh-ly-bom-xit-dau-nam-2019-180-201017.html\">Barca s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng thanh l\u00fd \u201cbom x\u1ecbt\u201d \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2019</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5595","checkdouble":"202157"},{"date":"11:13 13/11","title":"V\u01b0\u1ee3t Indonesia, Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 2 trong b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng t\u1ed5ng \u0111i\u1ec3m AFF Cup","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/11/9/vuot-indonesia-viet-nam-dung-thu-2-trong-bang-xep-hang-tong-diem-aff-cup.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>S\u1ee9c n\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn ng\u00e0y 16/11 t\u1edbi \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean r\u1ea5t cao, khi HLV Malaysia tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 3 v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nMalaysia kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m cao \u0111\u1ed9<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div>V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2 b\u1ea3ng A, \u0110T Malaysia \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng sau m\u00e0n ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n \u0110T L\u00e0o. D\u00f9 b\u1ecb ch\u1ecdc th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t s\u1edbm, nh\u01b0ng Malaysia \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c 3-1.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Tan Cheng Hoe \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0110T Campuchia trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng 1-0, v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean cho ng\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng A c\u00f9ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn s\u1eafp t\u1edbi di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh s\u1ebd v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Chia s\u1ebb sau m\u00e0n l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc L\u00e0o, HLV c\u1ee7a Malaysia cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. D\u00f9 b\u1ecb ch\u1ecdc th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1eabn cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 ki\u00ean tr\u00ec v\u00e0 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Malaysia tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Vi\u1ec7t Nam\" title=\"HLV Tan Cheng Hoe c\u1ee7a Malaysia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/11/13/thuyen-truong-malaysia-khang-dinh-se-choi-tan-cong-truoc-viet-nam.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Malaysia tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Vi\u1ec7t Nam</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n&ldquo;Hy v\u1ecdng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec tinh th\u1ea7n n\u00e0y \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn ti\u1ebfp theo v\u1edbi Vi\u1ec7t Nam, d\u00f9 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 trong 90 ph\u00fat. \u0110T Malaysia s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ghi b\u00e0n, qua \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00e0nh tr\u1ecdn 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m&rdquo; &ndash; HLV Malaysia tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>D\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u nay, Malaysia s\u1ebd \u0111\u1eb7t ch\u00e2n t\u1edbi H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 16/11. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 v\u1edbi l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t 2, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp trong 2 ng\u00e0y v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t sau bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp ng\u00e0y 12/11 c\u1ee7a \u0110T<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/vuot-indonesia-viet-nam-dung-thu-2-trong-bang-xep-hang-tong-diem-aff-cup-168-202158.html\">V\u01b0\u1ee3t Indonesia, Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 2 trong b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng t\u1ed5ng \u0111i\u1ec3m AFF Cup</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/dan-thu-mon-dt-viet-nam-tap-cang-truoc-tran-gap-malaysia-292-202121.html\">B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng t\u1eadp ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3 v\u1edbi v\u0169 kh\u00ed s\u00fat xa c\u1ee7a Malaysia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/cong-phuong-hoa-sieu-xayda-trong-bai-tap-but-toc-dt-viet-nam-292-202119.html\">C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00f3a Si\u00eau Xay-da trong b\u00e0i t\u1eadp b\u1ee9t t\u1ed1c c\u1ee7a \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-pho-dien-ky-thuat-trong-buoi-tap-cua-dt-viet-nam-292-202116.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp c\u1ee7a \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/doan-van-hau-tra-loi-phong-van-cuc-run-trong-lan-dau-du-aff-168-202115.html\">\u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n c\u1ef1c run trong l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u d\u1ef1 AFF</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5594","checkdouble":"202158"},{"date":"10:54 13/11","title":"Real Madrid ch\u01b0a t\u1eeb b\u1ecf sao s\u00e1ng Nam M\u1ef9","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/11/13/real-madrid-muon-mua-juan-quintero.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Juan Quintero. CLB Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Colombia, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf World Cup 2018.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Real t\u1eebng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Quintero</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, Juan Quintero \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T Colombia. Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh James Rodriguez li\u00ean t\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 25 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 cung c\u1ea5p s\u1ef1 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh t\u1ed1t (ch\u1ec9 cao 1m68) song Quintero c\u00f3 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng pha \u0111i b\u00f3ng l\u1eaft l\u00e9o. T\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, anh c\u00f3 1 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 2 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o sau 4 tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Juan Quintero c\u1ee7a River h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Juan Quintero c\u1ee7a River h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/11/13/real-madrid-muon-mua-juan-quintero.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Juan Quintero th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nK\u1ebft th\u00fac chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m d\u00e0nh cho Quintero. Trong \u0111\u00f3, Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Juan Quintero v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eed \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n t\u1edbi g\u1eb7p River Plate. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00ednh t\u1edbi l\u00fac \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Argentina \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111i v\u00e0o giai \u0111o\u1ea1n n\u01b0\u1edbc r\u00fat t\u1ea1i Copa Libertadores v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n nh\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ea1i th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Quintero sau World Cup 2018 c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i cho River. Anh m\u1edbi gia nh\u1eadp g\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 Argentina \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2018 t\u1eeb Porto d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n 1 n\u0103m. \u0110\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m sau, h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng gi\u1eefa \u0111\u00f4i b\u00ean s\u1ebd h\u1ebft h\u1ea1n v\u00e0 River c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n mua \u0111\u1ee9t Quintero v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 5 tri\u1ec7u Euro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n tr\u1ea3 anh v\u1ec1 Porto ho\u1eb7c \u0111em b\u00e1n lu\u00f4n cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c kh\u00e1c. Real Madrid n\u1eb1m trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3. \u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Quintero l\u00e0 Rodrigo Riep t\u1eebng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha t\u1eebng li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Real sau khi chia tay Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111ang r\u1ea5t thi\u1ebfu nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn. T\u1edbi s\u00e2n Santiago Bernabeu, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n s\u1eafc s\u1ea3o, nh\u1eefng c\u00fa s\u00fat xa tr\u00e1i ph\u00e1 hay nh\u1eefng qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t h\u00f3c hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Quinteto c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft s\u1ef1 b\u1ebf t\u1eafc n\u01a1i ti\u1ec1n tuy\u1ebfn Los Blancos.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-co-doi-thu-lon-vu-iago-aspas-180-202102.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/24/real-co-doi-thu-lon-vu-iago-aspas.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-co-doi-thu-lon-vu-iago-aspas-180-202102.html\">Real c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn v\u1ee5 h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i Liverpool</span><br>\r\n<span>Napoli mu\u1ed1n mua Iago Aspas c\u1ee7a Celta Vigo, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Real Madrid trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-co-the-mua-3-tan-binh-o-phien-cho-dong-2019-180-201981.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/11/8/real-co-the-mua-3-tan-binh-o-phien-cho-dong-2019.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-co-the-mua-3-tan-binh-o-phien-cho-dong-2019-180-201981.html\">Real c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mua 3 t\u00e2n binh \u1edf phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 \u0110\u00f4ng 2019</span><br>\r\n<span>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid s\u1ebd ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u00f4i n\u1ed5i v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m 2019, theo Marca, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7, m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n...</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-khong-goi-lai-bom-tan-45-trieu-euro-vao-thang-1-180-201912.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/11/10/real-khong-goi-lai-bom-tan-45-trieu-euro-vao-thang-1.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-khong-goi-lai-bom-tan-45-trieu-euro-vao-thang-1-180-201912.html\">Real kh\u00f4ng g\u1ecdi l\u1ea1i \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d 45 tri\u1ec7u euro v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1</span><br>\r\n<span>Rodrygo kh\u00f4ng t\u1edbi Real Madrid v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m 2019, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 17 tu\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e1 cho Santos \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00edch l\u0169y th\u00eam kinh nghi\u1ec7m.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5593","checkdouble":"202159"},{"date":"11:25 13/11","title":"Juventus mu\u1ed1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/11/13/juventus-muon-mua-jadon-sancho.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Jadon Sancho. Sao tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh c\u1ee7a Borussia Dortmund \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfn th\u1ea7n t\u1ed1c v\u00e0 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 t\u1ea1i Bundesliga.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Sancho t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i Dortmund</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJadon Sancho t\u1eebng l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a h\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n Man City v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao. Tuy nhi\u00ean, cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Etihad l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t v\u00e0 sao tr\u1ebb n\u00e0y quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean trong c\u00e1c s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ec9nh cao.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, Sancho gia nh\u1eadp Borussia Dortmund v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 8 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u00e1ng su\u1ed1t d\u00e0nh cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 2000. T\u1ea1i CLB m\u1edbi, Sancho l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00f4n l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i 1 v\u00e0 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 th\u1ea5y r\u00f5.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Jadon Sancho c\u1ee7a Dortmund h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Jadon Sancho c\u1ee7a Dortmund h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/11/13/juventus-muon-mua-jadon-sancho.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Jadon Sancho ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i Dortmund</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng bi\u1ec3u hi\u1ec7n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh n\u00e0y th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n. \u0110\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i t\u1edbi m\u00f9a 2018/19, Sancho khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea3 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u ph\u1ea3i ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u1ebfn m\u00ecnh. T\u00ednh t\u1edbi l\u00fac n\u00e0y, anh ra s\u00e2n 15 l\u1ea7n cho Dortmund t\u1ea1i Bundesliga v\u00e0 Champions League, \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 5 b\u00e0n c\u00f9ng 7 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e1ng n\u00f3i trong 15 tr\u1eadn tr\u00ean, c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 7 l\u00e0 t\u1eeb gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 788 ph\u00fat tr\u00ean s\u00e2n. Trung b\u00ecnh c\u1ee9 65.6 ph\u00fat, Sancho l\u1ea1i tham gia tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Dortmund.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c Juventus \u0111\u1ec3 \u00fd</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng, Sancho \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi l\u00ean \u0110T Anh th\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Sao tr\u1ebb n\u00e0y l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Gareth Southgate trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra m\u1eaft tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 UEFA Nations League ng\u00e0y 13/10. Qua \u0111\u00f3, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/jadon-sancho-lap-ky-luc-tai-dt-anh-184-199396.html\" target=\"_blank\">Sancho l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c</span> c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb nh\u1ea5t ra m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1955 t\u1edbi nay (18 tu\u1ed5i 183 ng\u00e0y).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/nhan-vat/marco-reus-va-jadon-sancho-hay-la-ban-tinh-ca-tron-ven-389-201435.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/11/5/marco-reus-va-jadon-sancho-hay-la-ban-tinh-ca-tron-ven.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/nhan-vat/marco-reus-va-jadon-sancho-hay-la-ban-tinh-ca-tron-ven-389-201435.html\">Marco Reus v\u00e0 Jadon Sancho: H\u00e3y l\u00e0 b\u1ea3n t\u00ecnh ca tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n!</span><br>\r\n<span>\u0110\u00e3 r\u1ea5t l\u00e2u r\u1ed3i nh\u1eefng c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00f9ng Ruhr m\u1edbi s\u1ed1ng trong nh\u1eefng th\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y t\u01b0\u01a1i \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf. Khi \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd, ng\u01b0\u1eddi lu\u00f4n xem Dortmund l\u00e0...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1edf l\u1ea1i CLB, Sancho ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao. M\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, anh ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ee7 90 ph\u00fat trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng quan tr\u1ecdng 3-2 c\u1ee7a Dortmund tr\u01b0\u1edbc Bayern Munich t\u1ea1i Bundesliga. V\u00e0 theo nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin m\u00e0 Calciomercato c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, tr\u00ean kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i s\u00e2n Westfalen h\u00f4m \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tuy\u1ec3n tr\u1ea1ch vi\u00ean t\u1eeb kh\u1eafp ch\u00e2u \u00c2u bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ea1i gia Juventus c\u1ee7a Italia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nJuventus mu\u1ed1n mua Jadon Sancho nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n l\u00e2u d\u00e0i cho h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng. C\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 m\u00e0 Bianconeri ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 nh\u1ecf ch\u00fat n\u00e0o. S\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Sancho \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a anh t\u0103ng l\u00ean phi m\u00e3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 s\u1edbm c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh, Juventus d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1eb7t l\u00ean b\u00e0n \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 80 tri\u1ec7u Euro (70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng). H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Sancho v\u1edbi Dortmund c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n t\u1edbi t\u1eadn n\u0103m 2022.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5592","checkdouble":"202160"}]}
