{"data":[{"date":"18:17 26/07","title":"T\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng khi giao h\u1eefu, c\u1eb7p sao Tottenham \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u201cth\u01b0\u1edfng n\u00f3ng\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/26/hlv-pochettino-phat-bieu-ve-llorente-va-lucas.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Pochettino ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Llorente v\u00e0 Lucas. \u00d4ng h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd t\u01b0\u1edfng th\u01b0\u1edfng cho h\u1ecd c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf Premier League sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Roma trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Llorente v\u00e0 Lucas t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Roma</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tottenham m\u1edbi c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi 2018/19. H\u1ecd giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi AS Roma trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u th\u01b0\u1eddng ni\u00ean International Champions Cup. B\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u00e0n so t\u00e0i n\u00e0y, Spurs v\u1eafng 9 th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 Harry Kane v\u00e0 Dele Alli do \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gia h\u1ea1n ngh\u1ec9 ph\u00e9p sau World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 v\u1eady, v\u1edbi l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng hi\u1ec7n c\u00f3, Tottenham v\u1eabn \u0111\u00e8 b\u1eb9p Roma 4-1. Trong \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng Fernando Llorente v\u00e0 Lucas Moura l\u00e0 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t. C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t 3 b\u00e0n tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Pochettino ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Llorente v\u00e0 Lucas h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Pochettino ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Llorente v\u00e0 Lucas h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/hlv-pochettino-phat-bieu-ve-llorente-va-lucas.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Llorente v\u00e0 Lucas t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Roma</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c Pochettino ca ng\u1ee3i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Mauricio Pochettino r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Llorente v\u00e0 Lucas \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m. \u00d4ng hy v\u1ecdng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 n\u00e0y trong nh\u1eefng tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi khi thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c. &ldquo;M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t so v\u1edbi m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ef1 World Cup. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, t\u00f4i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi c\u00e1c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. C\u1ea3 Llorente v\u00e0 Lucas \u0111\u1ec1u khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng. H\u1ecd \u0111ang t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i&rdquo;, HLV Pochettino ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Llorente v\u00e0 Lucas.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pochettino\" title=\"Pochettino\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/14/Mauricio-Pochettino-thay-the-Antonio-Conte-dan-dat-Chelsea-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>HLV Pochettino ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Llorente v\u00e0 Lucas v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 khen ng\u1ee3i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng, Pochettino n\u00f3i th\u00eam: &ldquo;\u0110\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i theo c\u00e1ch n\u00e0y s\u1ebd kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. T\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i th\u00edch \u1ee9ng v\u1edbi ho\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh. H\u1ecd c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i&rdquo;, chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina n\u00f3i th\u00eam.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i sau h\u01a1n 10 th\u00e1ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u. H\u1ecd c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 h\u01a1n 20 ng\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. S\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i h\u01a1n nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i n\u00f3.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Tottenham tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tottenham-muon-tai-ngo-modric-172-191894.html\">Tottenham mu\u1ed1n t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Modric</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-to-long-thuong-hai-tottenham-172-191867.html\">Klopp t\u1ecf l\u00f2ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u1ea1i Tottenham</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/harry-kane-noi-gi-khi-tottenham-quyet-dinh-dung-ngoai-ttcn-172-191864.html\">Harry Kane n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi Tottenham quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ee9ng ngo\u00e0i TTCN?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-noi-gi-ve-viec-mu-chi-50-trieu-bang-mua-alderweireld-172-191725.html\">Mourinho n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c MU chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Alderweireld?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/zaha-muon-roi-crystal-palace-va-tin-vui-cho-tottenham-172-191673.html\">Sao ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh NHA b\u00e1o tin vui cho Tottenham</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1661","checkdouble":"192084"},{"date":"18:20 26/07","title":"5 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u MU 1-1 AC Milan","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/26/5-diem-nhan-sau-tran-dau-mu-11-ac-milan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sanchez l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edf t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi Suso c\u00f3 b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a ch\u1ec9 \u00edt ph\u00fat sau. T\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 1-1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1eef \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u00e0 Man United l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c sau lo\u1ea1t s\u00fat penalty. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>Sanchez ch\u01a1i xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"5 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u MU 1-1 AC Milan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"5 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u MU 1-1 AC Milan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Sanchez t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1eafm</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Martial r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi tour du \u0111\u1ea5u M\u1ef9 c\u1ee7a Man United, HLV Jose Mourinho coi nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 n\u00e0o tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng. Lukaku v\u00e0 Rashford \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 sau khi \u0111i t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a World Cup 2018. V\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn cho h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, HLV Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft b\u00e0i to\u00e1n nan gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Sanchez trong vai tr\u00f2 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1eafm. V\u00e0 ch\u00ednh ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 \u1edf ph\u00fat 12 khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i c\u1ee7a Mata.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSanchez l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/video/video-tong-hop-mu-11-pen-98-ac-milan-icc-2018-329-192065.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU 1-1 AC&nbsp;Milan</span>. Anh li\u00ean t\u1ee5c t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho AC Milan v\u1edbi t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng di chuy\u1ec3n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. V\u00e0 v\u1edbi m\u00f9a h\u00e8 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i sau 9 n\u0103m, Sanchez \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n r\u00f5 s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1t khao chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t ngu\u1ed3n n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u1ed3i d\u00e0o \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u00f3 tin.</div>\r\n<h2>H\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a MU b\u1ecb ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hang thu MU\" title=\"H\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 MU\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>H\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 MU b\u1ecb ph\u00e1 th\u1ee7ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt 3 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Milan. Nh\u01b0ng k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 ngay \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 15 khi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Axel Tuanzebe \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ed5ng Suso trong khi Eric Bailly v\u00e0 Chris Smalling thi \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u00e1 l\u01a1 l\u00e0 n\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 cho ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Milan tho\u00e1t b\u1eaby vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Man United c\u0169ng qu\u00e1 ch\u1eadm ch\u1ea1p trong t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng b\u1ecb th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi n\u00e0y. Suso th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1edd b\u00f3ng n\u1ea3y m\u1ed9t nh\u1ecbp tr\u01b0\u1edbc tung c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00e1i ph\u00e1 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Lee Grant.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMourinho c\u00f3 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ef1c t\u1ee9c v\u1edbi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 khi \u0111\u1ec3 thua \u1edf t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y. Ngay sau khi Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n thua, chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0111\u00e3 quay sang khu v\u1ef1c hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u1eed ch\u1ec9 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 gi\u1eadn d\u1eef. Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd Mourinho s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 \u1edf h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1.</div>\r\n<h2>Darmian \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri \u00e2n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Darmian\" title=\"Darmian\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/181449-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Darmian n\u1eafm gi\u1eef b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Antonio Valencia b\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, HLV Mourinho bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0a ra s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn kh\u00e1c \u0111eo b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a MU. Nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u1edbn \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra khi Darmian \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e3nh tr\u1ecdng tr\u00e1ch n\u00e0y \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p AC Milan thay v\u00ec nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u00e2m ni\u00ean kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0 Smalling hay Mata.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea3 hai h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a Man United l\u00e0 Valencia v\u00e0 Diogo Dalot \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, Darmian nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i cho \u0111\u1ebfn sau khi tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Milan, Darmian \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00e2ng cao nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n v\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i trong vai tr\u00f2 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00f4ng bi\u00ean. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1edbi Darmian khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ef1c k\u00e9m. N\u1ebfu gi\u1eef Darmian trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n Premier League, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Mourinho s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i xoay v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh 4 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng.</div>\r\n<h2>Shaw kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi Mourinho\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Shaw\" title=\"Shaw\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/4.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Shaw ch\u01a1i m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc AC&nbsp;Milan</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u0169ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 Darmian, Luke Shaw nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. S\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a MU \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i l\u00e0 Ashley Young \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i th\u00eam sau World Cup 2018. Marcos Rojo c\u0169ng v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t trong khi Daley Blind \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Ajax.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nShaw \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh. H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a anh v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMourinho v\u1eabn \u0111ang gi\u1eef ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o Luke Shaw, d\u00f9 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean c\u00f4ng khai ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. Shaw \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u 74 ph\u00fat nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1eadm ch\u00ed, Shaw c\u00f2n l\u00e0m m\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. Anh b\u1ecb thay ra sau m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eb7t Mourinho. Sau \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111i th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3 v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean trong ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Manchester.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nShaw v\u1eabn c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c HLV Mourinho v\u1ec1 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9ng minh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng, Shaw g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi Old Trafford sau m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem video tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u MU&nbsp;1-1 AC&nbsp;Milan:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/26/MU-1-1-Milan.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1660","checkdouble":"192085"},{"date":"13:20 26/07","title":"B\u00e1c s\u0129 n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/26/bac-si-noi-gi-ve-chan-thuong-cua-cong-phuong-xuan-manh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, b\u00e1c s\u0129 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng n\u00ean 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c trong \u00edt ng\u00e0y n\u1eefa.</h2><h2>Ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng ng\u1ea1i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"B\u00e1c s\u0129 n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"B\u00e1c s\u0129 n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/cong-phuong-chan-thuong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh s\u1ebd s\u1edbm b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c do ch\u1ec9 g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u1eb9</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1eadp trung chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018 l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn 3 ca ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Tr\u1ecbnh V\u0103n L\u1ee3i, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh. Trong s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 b\u1edfi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t quan tr\u1ecdng t\u1ea1i \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u00e1 qu\u00e2n ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 1 v\u1eeba qua.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa SLNA v\u00e0 HAGL cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc sau m\u1ed9t n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c truy c\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. Sau khi ki\u1ec3m tra, c\u00e1c b\u00e1c s\u0129 k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh b\u1ecb l\u1eadt c\u1ed5 ch\u00e2n. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 qu\u00ea Y\u00ean Th\u00e0nh, Ngh\u1ec7 An kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i C\u00fap Qu\u1ed1c Gia 2018 gi\u1eefa FLC Thanh H\u00f3a vs SLNA. Thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, anh \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edbm l\u00ean t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf Trung t\u00e2m PVF t\u1ea1i H\u01b0ng Y\u00ean trong ng\u00e0y 25/7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ecb d\u00e3n d\u00e2y ch\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i sau bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Tuy nhi\u00ean ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2n s\u00fat x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1c s\u0129 Tr\u1ea7n Anh Tu\u1ea5n chia s\u1ebb: \u201cC\u00e1c em n\u00f3 ch\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn mai l\u00e0 t\u1eadp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i th\u00f4i, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec \u0111\u00e2u v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u0169ng nh\u1eb9 th\u00f4i m\u00e0. C\u00f2n ri\u00eang C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u00ec h\u00f4m nay \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadp c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ed3i\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1c g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t quan tr\u1ecdng kh\u00f4ng d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tin kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 vui h\u01a1n v\u1edbi HLV Park Hang Seo. Theo k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd r\u00e8n qu\u00e2n \u1edf Trung t\u00e2m PVF t\u1eeb nay cho \u0111\u1ebfn 31/8. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ebfn ng\u00e0y 1/8, \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho gi\u1ea3i T\u1ee9 H\u00f9ng di\u1ec5n ra tr\u00ean s\u00e2n M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh. \u1ede gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t g\u1eb7p Palestine (3/8), Oman (5/8) v\u00e0 Uzbekistan (7/8). \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o ASIAD 2018.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bui-tien-dung-va-nhung-cau-thu-u23-co-nguy-co-phai-ngoi-du-bi-tai-asiad-2018-168-192063.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/22/bui-tien-dung-va-nhung-cau-thu-u23-co-nguy-co-phai-ngoi-du-bi-tai-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bui-tien-dung-va-nhung-cau-thu-u23-co-nguy-co-phai-ngoi-du-bi-tai-asiad-2018-168-192063.html\">B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23 c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh trong th\u1eddi gian qua, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a \u0110T U23 c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb t\u1ea1i...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cong-phuong-tu-tin-se-co-suat-da-chinh-tai-asiad-2018-168-192064.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/26/cong-phuong-tu-tin-se-co-suat-da-chinh-tai-asiad-2018.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cong-phuong-tu-tin-se-co-suat-da-chinh-tai-asiad-2018-168-192064.html\">C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 tin s\u1ebd c\u00f3 su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng s\u00e1ng 26/7, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Nguy\u1ec5n C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u00e0n anh \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ebfm su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1659","checkdouble":"192066"},{"date":"16:04 26/07","title":"Pep Guardiola khen ng\u1ee3i h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ec3 thua Liverpool","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/26/pep-guardiola-khen-ngoi-hoc-tro-du-de-thua-liverpool.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Pep Guardiola \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen cho h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 sau khi \u0111\u1ec3 thua Liverpool \u1edf gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu ICC v\u1eeba qua.</h2><h2>Man City thua \u0111\u1eafng Liverpool\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pep Guardiola khen ng\u1ee3i h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ec3 thua Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Pep Guardiola khen ng\u1ee3i h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ec3 thua Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/pep-guardiola-khen-ngoi-hoc-tro-du-de-thua-liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Pep Guardiola khen ng\u1ee3i h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/video/video-tong-hop-liverpool-21-man-city-icc-2018-326-192055.html\" target=\"_blank\">Man City \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn tr\u1eadn thua th\u1ee9 2 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i ICC</span> khi Sadio Mane ghi b\u00e0n t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5m penalty \u1edf ph\u00fat 90+4.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng v\u00ec World Cup 2018 khi\u1ebfn s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Man xanh b\u1ecb gi\u1ea3m \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, The Citizens v\u1eabn l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1edd t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Leroy Sane. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ee9t t\u1ed1c v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Van Dijk v\u00e0 Clyne \u0111\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1 b\u00e0n d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc cho Man City.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a ch\u1ec9 6 ph\u00fat sau khi Salah v\u00e0o s\u00e2n t\u1eeb gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. \u0110\u1ebfn ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd, Mane \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh ghi b\u00e0n tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t penalty mang v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c cho Liverpool.</div>\r\n<h2>Pep Guardiola khen ng\u1ee3i h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Pep Guardiola kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng h\u01a1n v\u1edbi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 d\u00f9 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u1ecd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c sau c\u00f9ng l\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cTh\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. 75 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00e0 qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ea1nh tranh cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc. T\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1eabn d\u1eaft nh\u1eefng ch\u00e0ng trai n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTrong 75 ph\u00fat tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi \u0111\u00f3, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u00f9 m\u1ec7t l\u1ea3 nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ch\u1ea1y h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh. V\u00e0 trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o s\u00e2n nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. H\u1ecd x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong th\u1eddi gian cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNh\u01b0ng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i trung b\u00ecnh ch\u1eafc ch\u1ec9 18 hay 19. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Man City:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-man-city-12-liverpool-du-the-nao-kop-van-khong-the-thieu-king-172-192057.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Man City 1-2 Liverpool: D\u00f9 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o, Kop v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu King</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-liverpool-21-man-city-icc-2018-326-192055.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Liverpool 2-1 Man City (ICC 2018)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1658","checkdouble":"192069"},{"date":"14:53 26/07","title":"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u00e0y 26/7: Mourinho mu\u1ed1n t\u1ed1ng kh\u1ee9 Martial v\u00ec v\u00f4 k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/ngay-hom-nay-267.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u00f9 b\u1ecb nghi ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng, c\u1ed9ng th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n xung quanh vi\u1ec7c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, trung v\u1ec7 Smalling s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i Man United.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nSmalling kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i t\u00e2n binh<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00eam 2 t\u00e2n binh, t\u1eeb gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ebfn khi k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i. M\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7. V\u00e0 trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Old Trafford, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn Harry Maguire v\u00e0 Toby Alderweireld.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00fac n\u00e0y, Chris Smalling v\u00e0 Eric Bailly \u0111ang ch\u01a1i trong tour du \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf, trong khi b\u1ed9 ba Jones &ndash; Lindelof &ndash; Rojo \u0111i ngh\u1ec9 sau k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018. C\u00e1c ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh cho r\u1eb1ng, trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina Marcos Rojo \u0111ang lo ng\u1ea1i t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb trong bu\u1ed5i ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n, Chris Smalling l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y. Anh cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;C\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng m\u00e0 n\u00f3i, t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n tr\u1ea3i qua nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u nh\u01b0 v\u1eady h\u00e0ng n\u0103m. CLB n\u00e0y lu\u00f4n li\u00ean k\u1ebft v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng trung v\u1ec7 kh\u00e1c nhau, d\u00f9 l\u00e0 h\u1ecfi mua th\u1eadt hay tin \u0111\u1ed3n v\u00f4 c\u0103n c\u1ee9, r\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t s\u1ebd mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2y.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Smalling s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i M.U\" title=\"Smalling vs Tottenham\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/23/smalling-khong-dem-xia-den-viec-mu-mua-them-trung-ve.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Smalling s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i M.U</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n&ldquo;Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 lo l\u1eafng b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec, t\u00f4i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i M.U v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh, b\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u00eam c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y. T\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u quen thu\u1ed9c trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i qua, gi\u1eef chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t&rdquo; &ndash; Chris Smalling t\u1ef1 tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 h\u00e8 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi anh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham d\u1ef1 World Cup: &ldquo;R\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, b\u1edfi v\u00ec b\u1ea1n lu\u00f4n mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn. D\u00f9 sao, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1i \u0111a k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m m\u1edbi b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n, s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Smalling s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng. B\u1edfi cho d\u00f9 c\u00f3 hay kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng bom t\u1ea5n v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh s\u1edf h\u1eefu tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cao nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-mu-11-pen-98-ac-milan-icc-2018-329-192065.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/26/video-tong-hop-mu-11-pen-98-ac-milan-icc-2018.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-mu-11-pen-98-ac-milan-icc-2018-329-192065.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: MU 1-1 (pen 9-8) AC Milan (ICC 2018)</span><br>\r\nC\u00f3 b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 s\u1edbm do c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Alexis Sanchez nh\u01b0ng Man Utd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 1-1 sau 90 ph\u00fat tr\u01b0\u1edbc Milan v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i sau \u0111\u1ebfn 13 l\u01b0\u1ee3t s\u00fat lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-giuc-mu-mua-maguire-172-192058.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/20/mourinho-giuc-mu-mua-maguire.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-giuc-mu-mua-maguire-172-192058.html\">Mourinho gi\u1ee5c l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o M.U mua g\u1ea5p sao tuy\u1ec3n Anh</span><br>\r\nMourinho gi\u1ee5c l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o M.U mua Maguire. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1t m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ni\u1ec1m tin t\u1eeb...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1657","checkdouble":"192070"},{"date":"15:52 26/07","title":"Mourinho \u0111e d\u1ecda Liverpool v\u1ec1 hi\u1ec3m h\u1ecda m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/26/mourinho-de-doa-liverpool-ve-hiem-hoa-mua-bong-moi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng qu\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, HLV Mourinho c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Klopp bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0a Liverpool \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nMourinho ghen t\u1ef5 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf qu\u00e1 ch\u1eadm ch\u1ea1p tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, The Kop \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u0111em v\u1ec1 4 t\u00e2n binh kh\u1ee7ng trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y cho th\u1ea5y tham v\u1ecdng gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf, \u0111i\u1ec1u M.U ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do, Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111em nh\u1eefng \u00e1p l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0o Jurgen Klopp.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Mourinho cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n, n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0, t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n h\u1ebft l\u00e0 b\u1ea1n n\u00ean c\u00f3 s\u1eb5n t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh trong ng\u00e2n h\u00e0ng. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u00e0 b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 h\u1ecd \u0111ang l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. M\u1ecdi t\u00e2n binh Liverpool \u0111em v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, t\u00f4i m\u1eebng cho h\u1ecd.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, s\u1ebd l\u00e0 d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u khi b\u1ea1n y\u00eau c\u1ea7u h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 chi ti\u00eau. H\u1ecd ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng gi\u00eang v\u1edbi Virgil Van Dijk, \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Klopp v\u1ec1 \u00e1p l\u1ef1c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch\" title=\"Mourinho c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Klopp\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/mourinho-de-doa-liverpool-ve-hiem-hoa-mua-bong-moi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Klopp v\u1ec1 \u00e1p l\u1ef1c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\nQuay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0, Mourinho chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng: &ldquo;V\u00e2ng, Darmian \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i. V\u00e0 khi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, n\u1ebfu CLB nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn, b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i t\u1ecf ra nh\u00e2n \u0111\u1ea1o v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng nhu c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i ra \u0111i b\u1eb1ng b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 gi\u00e1 n\u00e0o. Cho \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1edd, nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb d\u00e0nh cho Darmian l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn.&rdquo;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Valencia \u0111ang ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 s\u1ebd b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, Dalot c\u0169ng v\u1eady. Young v\u00e0 Lindelof c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i, d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i s\u1ebd th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a, Darmian ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. B\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Qua nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Mourinho c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Klopp bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 s\u1ef1 ghen t\u1ef5 khi \u00f4ng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u00f3 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh, nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/smalling-khong-dem-xia-den-viec-mu-mua-them-trung-ve-172-192073.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/23/smalling-khong-dem-xia-den-viec-mu-mua-them-trung-ve.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/smalling-khong-dem-xia-den-viec-mu-mua-them-trung-ve-172-192073.html\">Smalling kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfm x\u1ec9a \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c M.U mua th\u00eam trung v\u1ec7</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 b\u1ecb nghi ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng, c\u1ed9ng th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n xung quanh vi\u1ec7c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, trung v\u1ec7 Smalling s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i Man United.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-giuc-mu-mua-maguire-172-192058.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/20/mourinho-giuc-mu-mua-maguire.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-giuc-mu-mua-maguire-172-192058.html\">Mourinho gi\u1ee5c l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o M.U mua g\u1ea5p sao tuy\u1ec3n Anh</span><br>\r\nMourinho gi\u1ee5c l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o M.U mua Maguire. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1t m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ni\u1ec1m tin t\u1eeb...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1656","checkdouble":"192071"},{"date":"15:57 26/07","title":"\u0110\u00e2y! Ng\u00f4i sao ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n c\u00e1nh c\u1eeda r\u1eddi M.U nh\u1ea5t","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/26/mourinh-xac-nhan-darmian-co-the-roi-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Jose Mourinho x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Darmian mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi M.U. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y x\u1ea3y ra b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 Antonio Valencia c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ee1 tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League b\u1edfi ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDarmian mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi M.U</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Matteo Darmian r\u1eddi Man United kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e2y gi\u1edd m\u1edbi xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1eeb ph\u00eda CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ed3i h\u01b0\u01a1ng ch\u01a1i cho Juventus. 1 n\u0103m tr\u00f4i qua, \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1edd anh v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh HLV Jose Mourinho.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Darmian \u0111\u00e3 mang b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng M.U \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi AC Milan t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup. Anh ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 \u1ed5n v\u00e0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m. Chung cu\u1ed9c, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Milan 9-9 \u1edf ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n sau khi h\u00f2a 1-1 \u1edf 2 hi\u1ec7p ch\u00ednh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Darmian mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi MU h\u00e8 n\u00e0y h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Mourinho x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Darmian mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi MU h\u00e8 n\u00e0y h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/mourinh-xac-nhan-darmian-co-the-roi-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Darmian \u0111eo b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng M.U tr\u01b0\u1edbc Milan</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn, Mourinho x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Darmian mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi M.U. \u201cB\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Darmian b\u1edfi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi trong 2 n\u0103m t\u00f4i d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi 1 d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\u1ec1n nhi\u1ec7m Van Gaal. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 ch\u00e0ng trai lu\u00f4n s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn h\u1ebft nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00ecnh c\u00f3, tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh t\u1eeb AC Milan v\u00e0 ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi CLB th\u1eddi th\u01a1 \u1ea5u\u201d, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha n\u00f3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cG\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i CLB c\u0169 v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111eo b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu mang nhi\u1ec1u \u00fd ngh\u0129a. Darmian mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i v\u00e0 t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 khi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng c\u01b0 x\u1eed c\u00f3 t\u00ecnh ng\u01b0\u1eddi.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n thay th\u1ebf</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDarmian \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Juventus v\u00e0 Inter Milan li\u00ean h\u1ec7 nh\u01b0ng Mourinho ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 M.U ch\u01b0a nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, c\u1ed9ng th\u00eam vi\u1ec7c Antonio Valencia \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9, vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho Darmian ra \u0111i v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1eef nguy\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Mourinho\" title=\"HLV Mourinho\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/HLV-Mourinho-cua-M.U.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Mourinho x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Darmian mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi M.U</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCho \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e2y gi\u1edd c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb ch\u00fang t\u00f4i nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho Darmian ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u01b0ng \u00fd\u201d, Mourinho n\u00f3i th\u00eam. \u201cValencia \u0111ang ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, Diogo Dalot c\u0169ng v\u1eady. H\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n t\u1ea1i Premier League.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, Mourinho ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 Ashley Young c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n sang \u0111\u00e1 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a M.U khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u. \u00d4ng s\u1ebd y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 33 tu\u1ed5i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u1edbm h\u01a1n d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1eadu World Cup 2018 khi c\u00f9ng \u0110T Anh v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cAshley Young c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i song \u0111ang \u0111i ngh\u1ec9. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng r\u00f5 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00ec t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n nay hay ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ngh\u1ec9 h\u00e8. Victor Lindelof c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n d\u00f9 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e1 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 2 t\u1edbi t\u1ea1i Manchester\u201d, Mourinho ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cV\u00ec v\u1eady, Darmian s\u1ebd ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb th\u00edch h\u1ee3p g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn. C\u00f2n n\u1ebfu \u1edf l\u1ea1i, \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng M.U tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/smalling-khong-dem-xia-den-viec-mu-mua-them-trung-ve-172-192073.html\">Smalling kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfm x\u1ec9a \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c M.U mua th\u00eam trung v\u1ec7</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-giuc-mu-mua-maguire-172-192058.html\">Mourinho gi\u1ee5c l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o M.U mua g\u1ea5p sao tuy\u1ec3n Anh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sao-mu-cam-thay-hanh-phuc-khi-co-hlv-moi-172-192053.html\">Sao M.U c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi c\u00f3 HLV m\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/tiet-lo-mu-va-real-tu-choi-mua-malcom-180-192001.html\">Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9: MU v\u00e0 Real t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i mua Malcom</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-muon-mua-bailey-thay-willian-172-191982.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! C\u00e1i t\u00ean Chelsea s\u1ebd mang v\u1ec1 n\u1ebfu b\u00e1n Willian cho M.U</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1655","checkdouble":"192072"},{"date":"15:15 26/07","title":"Smalling kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfm x\u1ec9a \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c M.U mua th\u00eam trung v\u1ec7","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/23/smalling-khong-dem-xia-den-viec-mu-mua-them-trung-ve.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u00f9 b\u1ecb nghi ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng, c\u1ed9ng th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n xung quanh vi\u1ec7c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, trung v\u1ec7 Smalling s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i Man United.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nSmalling kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i t\u00e2n binh<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00eam 2 t\u00e2n binh, t\u1eeb gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ebfn khi k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i. M\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7. V\u00e0 trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Old Trafford, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn Harry Maguire v\u00e0 Toby Alderweireld.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00fac n\u00e0y, Chris Smalling v\u00e0 Eric Bailly \u0111ang ch\u01a1i trong tour du \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf, trong khi b\u1ed9 ba Jones &ndash; Lindelof &ndash; Rojo \u0111i ngh\u1ec9 sau k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018. C\u00e1c ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh cho r\u1eb1ng, trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina Marcos Rojo \u0111ang lo ng\u1ea1i t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb trong bu\u1ed5i ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n, Chris Smalling l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y. Anh cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;C\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng m\u00e0 n\u00f3i, t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n tr\u1ea3i qua nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u nh\u01b0 v\u1eady h\u00e0ng n\u0103m. CLB n\u00e0y lu\u00f4n li\u00ean k\u1ebft v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng trung v\u1ec7 kh\u00e1c nhau, d\u00f9 l\u00e0 h\u1ecfi mua th\u1eadt hay tin \u0111\u1ed3n v\u00f4 c\u0103n c\u1ee9, r\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t s\u1ebd mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2y.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Smalling s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i M.U\" title=\"Smalling vs Tottenham\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/23/smalling-khong-dem-xia-den-viec-mu-mua-them-trung-ve.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Smalling s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i M.U</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n&ldquo;Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 lo l\u1eafng b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec, t\u00f4i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i M.U v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh, b\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u00eam c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y. T\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u quen thu\u1ed9c trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i qua, gi\u1eef chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t&rdquo; &ndash; Chris Smalling t\u1ef1 tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 h\u00e8 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi anh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham d\u1ef1 World Cup: &ldquo;R\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, b\u1edfi v\u00ec b\u1ea1n lu\u00f4n mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn. D\u00f9 sao, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1i \u0111a k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m m\u1edbi b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n, s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Smalling s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng. B\u1edfi cho d\u00f9 c\u00f3 hay kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng bom t\u1ea5n v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh s\u1edf h\u1eefu tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cao nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-mu-11-pen-98-ac-milan-icc-2018-329-192065.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/26/video-tong-hop-mu-11-pen-98-ac-milan-icc-2018.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-mu-11-pen-98-ac-milan-icc-2018-329-192065.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: MU 1-1 (pen 9-8) AC Milan (ICC 2018)</span><br>\r\nC\u00f3 b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 s\u1edbm do c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Alexis Sanchez nh\u01b0ng Man Utd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 1-1 sau 90 ph\u00fat tr\u01b0\u1edbc Milan v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i sau \u0111\u1ebfn 13 l\u01b0\u1ee3t s\u00fat lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-giuc-mu-mua-maguire-172-192058.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/20/mourinho-giuc-mu-mua-maguire.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-giuc-mu-mua-maguire-172-192058.html\">Mourinho gi\u1ee5c l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o M.U mua g\u1ea5p sao tuy\u1ec3n Anh</span><br>\r\nMourinho gi\u1ee5c l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o M.U mua Maguire. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1t m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ni\u1ec1m tin t\u1eeb...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1654","checkdouble":"192073"},{"date":"15:24 26/07","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Atletico Madrid vs Arsenal 18h35 ng\u00e0y 26/7 (ICC 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/26/atletico-madrid-vs-arsenal-tran-dau-icc-2018-ngay-hom-nay.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Atletico Madrid vs Arsenal: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Arsenal vs Atletico Madrid gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup ICC 2018 l\u00fac 18h35 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 26/7.</h2>(\u1ea5n Ctrl + F5 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n5 - L\u00e0 s\u1ed1 t\u00e2n binh m\u00e0 Arsenal mang \u0111\u1ebfn Sigapore \u0111\u1ec3 tham d\u1ef1 ICC. H\u1ecd g\u1ed3m Bernd Leno, Sokratis, Matteo Guendouzi, Emile Smith Rowe v\u00e0 Eddie Nketiah. Ri\u00eang t\u00e2n binh Lucas Torreira ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e1ng 8 m\u1edbi h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n v\u1edbi Arsenal.<br>\r\n<h2>TH\u00d4NG TIN XUNG QUANH</h2>\r\n- Theo t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 ch\u00e2u \u00c1, Atletico th\u1eafng 1, h\u00f2a 1/2 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y g\u1eb7p Arsenal. <br>\r\n- Theo t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 ch\u00e2u \u00c1, Atletico th\u1eafng 5, thua 2/7 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. <br>\r\n- Theo t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 ch\u00e2u \u00c1, Arsenal th\u1eafng 4, h\u00f2a 2, thua 2/8 tr\u1eadn m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n- 4 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Atletico c\u00f3 t\u1eeb 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u1edf l\u00ean trong hi\u1ec7p 1. C\u1ea3 6 tr\u1eadn m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Arsenal \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf hi\u1ec7p 1.<br>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1eb6C BI\u1ec6T</h2>\r\nL\u1ebb b\u00e0n th\u1eafng<br>\r\n2/3 l\u1ea7n g\u1eb7p nhau gi\u1eefa 2 \u0111\u1ed9i k\u1ebft th\u00fac l\u1ebb b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. 5/7 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Atletico c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 l\u1ebb. 4/6 tr\u1eadn m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Arsenal c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 chia h\u1ebft cho 2. Do v\u1eady, tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng k\u1ebft th\u00fac l\u1ebb b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:<br>\r\nAtletico Madrid: Oblak \u2013 Juanfran, Montero, Rodriguez, Solano \u2013 Garcia, Olabe, Partey, Vitolo \u2013 Vietto, Gameiro<br>\r\nArsenal: Leno \u2013 Bellerin, Mustafi, Sokratis, Kolasinac \u2013 Ramsey, Elneny \u2013 Mkhitaryan, Ozil, Aubameyang \u2013 Lacazette\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/14/Boreham-Wood-vs-Arsenal_mp4_Output_1.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1653","checkdouble":"192074"},{"date":"16:23 26/07","title":"Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c: Chelsea chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng trong khung g\u1ed7","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/26/chinh-thuc-chelsea-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-lao-tuong-trong-khung-go.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 38 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh Robert Green theo d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do c\u00f9ng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n m\u1ed9t n\u0103m.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Robert Green \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Huddersfield Town thanh l\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i y\u00ean v\u1ecb tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 38 tu\u1ed5i c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Stamford Bridge theo d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do v\u00e0 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n m\u1ed9t n\u0103m.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Robert Green theo d\u1ea1ng t\u1ef1 do h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Robert Green theo d\u1ea1ng t\u1ef1 do h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/chinh-thuc-chelsea-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-lao-tuong-trong-khung-go.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Robert Green theo d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Anh c\u0169ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Chelsea khi ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n ph\u00f2ng ng\u1eeba cho Thibaut Courtois v\u00e0 Willy Caballero, hay c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u1ea3 cho m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n t\u00e2n binh kh\u00e1c trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 ra \u0111i v\u00e0 gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">D\u00f9 sao th\u00ec v\u1edbi b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n x\u1ebf b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ebfn n\u01a1i n\u00e0y, Green c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u ph\u1ea5n kh\u1edfi c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Anh b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh \u1edf World Cup 2010 trong bu\u1ed5i l\u1ec5 ra m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cTh\u1eadt \u0111i\u00ean r\u1ed3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec x\u1ea3y ra trong 24 ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 v\u1eeba qua. T\u00f4i \u0111ang th\u1ea5t nghi\u1ec7p v\u00e0 ngh\u0129 suy \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1ec1 b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i ti\u1ebfp theo trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd ra sao, th\u1ebf r\u1ed3i m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i g\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y v\u1edbi n\u1ed9i dung ch\u1ee9a \u0111\u1ef1ng ng\u1eafn g\u1ecdn. Tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 Chelsea th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m vinh d\u1ef1 v\u00e0 t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi gia nh\u1eadp Chelsea, Green tr\u1ea3i qua 19 n\u0103m \u0111\u1ee9ng trong khung g\u1ed7 c\u00e1c CLB Norwich, West Ham, Queens Park Rangers, Leeds United v\u00e0 Huddersfield Town. Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 38 tu\u1ed5i t\u1eebng 12 l\u1ea7n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p, \u0111i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh l\u00e0 pha \u201c\u0111\u1ebb tr\u1ee9ng\u201d tai h\u1ea1i trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p M\u1ef9 \u1edf ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n World Cup 2010.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-bo-nhiem-sarri-chuong-su-moi-voi-ga-nhan-vien-ngan-hang-172-187380.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/30/chelsea-bo-nhiem-sarri-thu-thach-long-kien-nhan-voi-ga-nhan-vien-ngan-hang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-bo-nhiem-sarri-chuong-su-moi-voi-ga-nhan-vien-ngan-hang-172-187380.html\">Chelsea b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Sarri: Ch\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1eed m\u1edbi v\u1edbi g\u00e3 nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean ng\u00e2n h\u00e0ng</span><br>\r\nChelsea b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Sarri thay th\u1ebf HLV Conte trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng cao v\u00e0 qua \u0111\u00e2y, Stamford Bridge s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i, k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1652","checkdouble":"192075"},{"date":"17:01 26/07","title":"\u0110\u00e1 th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o, S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t c\u1ea5m thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ea3 m\u00f9a sau","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/26/da-tho-bao-sam-ngoc-duc-nhan-an-phat-cam-thi-dau-den-ca-mua-sau.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u00e1 th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch c\u00f3 h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng, S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t n\u1eb7ng t\u1eeb Ban k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt VFF khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a sau.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t<br />\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa CLB TP H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh vs Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 20 V-League 2018, S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c c\u00f3 pha v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o v\u1edbi Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ebf H\u01b0ng. Tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh r\u00fat th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf v\u1edbi S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c, c\u00f2n Th\u1ebf H\u01b0ng r\u1ea5t may kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sam Ngoc Duc nhan an phat cam thi dau den 8 tran.\" title=\"S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t c\u1ea5m thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ebfn 8 tr\u1eadn.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/da-tho-bao-sam-ngoc-duc-nhan-an-phat-cam-thi-dau-den-ca-mua-sau.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t c\u1ea5m thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ebfn 8 tr\u1eadn.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nSau v\u1ee5 vi\u1ec7c, Ban k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt VFF \u0111\u00e3 nh\u00f3m h\u1ecdp v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a ra \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t v\u1edbi S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a CLB TP.HCM b\u1ecb c\u1ea5m thi \u0111\u1ea5u 8 tr\u1eadn, ph\u1ea1t 35 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00ec c\u00f3 h\u00e0nh vi &quot;c\u1ed1 t\u00ecnh x\u00e2m ph\u1ea1m th\u00e2n th\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ebf H\u01b0ng&quot;.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c V-League 2018 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 6 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1eefa s\u1ebd k\u1ebft th\u00fac, S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd ngh\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft m\u00f9a. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n trong hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a sau v\u00ec \u00e1n treo gi\u00f2.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Li\u00ean t\u1ee5c nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t<br />\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c c\u0169ng b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2 8 tr\u1eadn khi c\u00f2n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i khi ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i v\u1edbi Anh H\u00f9ng (H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng). M\u00f9a n\u00e0y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u1ed1c Ngh\u1ec7 An c\u0169ng t\u1eebng ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i nguy hi\u1ec3m v\u1edbi \u0111\u00e0n em \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c khi ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n SLNA t\u1ea1i C\u00fap qu\u1ed1c gia.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau pha ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i \u0111\u00f3, S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2 4 tr\u1eadn. T\u00ednh t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn 6 th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng, 2 th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf. \u00d4ng Nguy\u1ec5n H\u1ea3i H\u01b0\u1eddng, tr\u01b0\u1edfng Ban k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt VFF tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c r\u0103n \u0111e b\u1edfi S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i nguy hi\u1ec3m m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch c\u00f3 h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng.</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nan-nhan-cua-sam-ngoc-duc-mong-muon-dieu-nay-sau-cu-dap-troi-giang-168-191901.html\">N\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y sau c\u00fa \u0111\u1ea1p tr\u1eddi gi\u00e1ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/vleague/sam-ngoc-duc-pham-loi-tho-bao-nhieu-lan-roi-291-191892.html\">S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n r\u1ed3i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/chu-tich-huu-thang-noi-gi-khi-sam-ngoc-duc-pham-loi-tho-bao-168-191885.html\">Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch H\u1eefu Th\u1eafng n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-miura-noi-gi-khi-chung-kien-hoc-tro-da-tho-bao-168-191820.html\">HLV Miura n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 b\u1ecb \u0111u\u1ed5i v\u00ec thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/vleague/clb-tphcm-keu-troi-vi-luc-luong-sam-ngoc-duc-duoc-giam-an-treo-gio-291-187003.html\">CLB TP.HCM k\u00eau tr\u1eddi v\u00ec l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3m \u00e1n treo gi\u00f2</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/vleague/sau-khi-cong-vinh-tu-chuc-thay-tro-hlv-miura-nhan-them-tin-du-291-185533.html\">Sau khi C\u00f4ng Vinh t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Miura nh\u1eadn th\u00eam tin d\u1eef</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1651","checkdouble":"192077"},{"date":"17:27 26/07","title":"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: 4 c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u1ea7n ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i Arsenal ngay l\u00fac n\u00e0y","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/26/goc-nhin-4-cai-ten-can-chung-to-minh-tai-arsenal-ngay-luc-nay.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau 22 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Arsene Wenger, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u1edf m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u1ea7n g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi HLV Unai Emery, trong tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Emirates.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nMesut Ozil<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng &ldquo;b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng&rdquo; cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng m\u00e0 Wenger th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n cho Arsenal, ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Mesut Ozil. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c bi\u1ebft r\u00f5 \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd ra \u0111i, nh\u01b0ng anh v\u1eabn quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a, Ozil \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai l\u00e2u d\u00e0i t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0 s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh cho Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau scandal t\u1eeb gi\u00e3 \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00ec b\u1ecb ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t s\u1eafc t\u1ed9c, Ozil \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Arsenal v\u1edbi v\u00f2ng tay c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. Unai Emery c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, v\u00e0 Arsenal l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a anh. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 trong bu\u1ed5i ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean khi nh\u1eadm ch\u1ee9c, Emery c\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u00e0i hoa n\u00e0y l\u00e0 h\u1ea1t nh\u00e2n trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u00f9ng nhau c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 2 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cam k\u1ebft, \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 Ozil c\u1ea7n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. H\u01a1n th\u1ebf n\u1eefa, anh c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc so v\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Unai Emery \u0111i \u0111\u00fang h\u01b0\u1edbng. B\u1edfi v\u1eady, \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a Mesut Ozil &ndash; m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u1ea7n g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi HLV Unai Emery h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 1\" title=\"nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u1ea7n g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi HLV Unai Emery h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/12/nhung-cai-ten-can-gay-an-tuong-voi-HLV-Unai-Emery-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mesut Ozil s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u00e1t ch\u1ee7 b\u00e0i c\u1ee7a Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h2>Bernd Leno<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1c trong khung g\u1ed7 v\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh thi\u1ebfu \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, Wenger \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 Petr Cech &ndash; m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u01b0ng d\u1ea7n b\u01b0\u1edbc sang b\u00ean kia s\u01b0\u1eddn d\u1ed1c. Emery bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, n\u00ean \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c Bernd Leno v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u00e0y s\u1ebd ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp theo.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngay t\u1eeb l\u00fac n\u00e0y ch\u1ee9 ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ebfn m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u, Leno ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng, v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng thay th\u1ebf l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng Petr Cech. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a anh s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ebfn k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong h\u01a1n 2 tu\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. Cech v\u00e0 Ospina l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng CLB kh\u00e1c, v\u00e0 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Leno s\u1ebd gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1p \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Leno kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c t\u1ea1o ra d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Emirates s\u1ebd gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i c\u1ea3 2. Khi \u0111\u00f3, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n binh 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, v\u00ec Premier League kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ch\u1ed7 cho nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u1ea7n g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi HLV Unai Emery h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Bernd Leno m\u1eb7c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 19 \u1edf Arsenal\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/tan-binh-bernd-leno-chinh-thuc-chon-so-ao-o-arsenal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Bernd Leno c\u1ea7n ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Lucas Perez<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ecb Wenger \u0111\u1ed1i x\u1eed thi\u1ebfu t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch t\u01b0\u1edbc \u00e1o s\u1ed1 9 cho Lacazette, c\u1ea3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua Perez b\u1ecb \u0111em cho Deportivo m\u01b0\u1ee3n. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a anh coi nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t, nh\u01b0ng sau t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 khi Deportivo xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a r\u00f5 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, v\u00e0 Emery \u0111ang xem x\u00e9t \u0111i\u1ec1n t\u00ean anh v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch 25 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 cho \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1edbi, ho\u1eb7c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ee9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t t\u00e2n HLV, Unai Emery mu\u1ed1n trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 th\u1eddi c\u01a1 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec3 Perez \u1edf l\u1ea1i, qua \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ee9u v\u00e3n s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u1ea7n g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi HLV Unai Emery h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"tien dao Lucas Perez\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/12/hang-thai-arsenal-co-cuu-canh-cho-su-nghiep.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Lucas Perez \u0111ang l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ecb l\u00e3ng qu\u00ean t\u1ea1i Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Aaron Ramsey<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales v\u1eabn \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Arsenal &ndash; v\u1ed1n ch\u1ec9 k\u00e9o d\u00e0i \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e1ng 6/2019. D\u00f9 m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai g\u1ea7n, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng n\u00e0o. Ramsey, v\u00ec v\u1eady ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra \u0111i trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u0103m nay.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p anh \u1edf l\u1ea1i, Ramsey c\u1ea7n ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng v\u1edbi Unai Emery, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169ng l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ca ng\u1ee3i v\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef anh l\u1ea1i. H\u01a1n th\u1ebf, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1990 c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean cho chi\u1ebfc b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng. C\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Mesut Ozil, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ee9ng minh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vai tr\u00f2 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u00e0u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh d\u01b0\u1edbi tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u1ea7n g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi HLV Unai Emery h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 4\" title=\"Ramsey\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/30/arsenal-nhan-tin-cuc-vui-tu-aaron-ramsey.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ramsey l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u1ea7n g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi HLV Unai Emery<span style=\"font-family: arial, verdana, \" lucida=\"\">&nbsp;</span></h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp theo, m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u1ea3 d\u0129 nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Arsenal s\u1ebd l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed Top 4. T\u1ea1i \u0111\u00f3, s\u1ebd c\u00f3 6 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ea1nh tranh quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t, v\u00e0 to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u1ea7n g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi HLV Unai Emery \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Champions League.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/atletico-madrid-vs-arsenal-tran-dau-icc-2018-ngay-hom-nay-372-192074.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/26/atletico-madrid-vs-arsenal-tran-dau-icc-2018-ngay-hom-nay.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/atletico-madrid-vs-arsenal-tran-dau-icc-2018-ngay-hom-nay-372-192074.html\">TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Atletico Madrid vs Arsenal 18h35 ng\u00e0y 26/7 (ICC 2018)</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Atletico Madrid vs Arsenal: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Arsenal vs Atletico Madrid gi\u1ea3i...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-chinh-thuc-len-tieng-ve-kha-nang-bi-milan-chat-dau-172-192042.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/24/arsenal-chinh-thuc-len-tieng-ve-kha-nang-bi-milan-chat-dau.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-chinh-thuc-len-tieng-ve-kha-nang-bi-milan-chat-dau-172-192042.html\">Arsenal ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb Milan ch\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ea7u</span><br>\r\nTrang ch\u1ee7 CLB th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u01b0a ra th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o b\u00e1c b\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chia tay gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh Ivan Gazidis v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1650","checkdouble":"192082"},{"date":"09:04 26/07","title":"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay (26/7/2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/26/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-hom-nay-2672018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>B\u1ecb anh em nh\u00e0 Neville cho r\u1eb1ng thi\u1ebfu chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p, l\u00e0 \u201cn\u1ed7i \u00f4 nh\u1ee5c\u201d c\u1ee7a Stoke, nh\u01b0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Shaqiri kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch c\u1ee7a huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nShaqiri ph\u1edbt l\u1edd ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m nay, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 \u0111\u00e3 gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 13 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, kh\u00e1 r\u1ebb cho t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a anh. S\u1edf d\u0129 c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y, b\u1edfi Stoke \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng v\u00e0 m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Shaqiri \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3m xu\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. M\u1ed9t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 qu\u00e1 h\u1eddi, m\u00e0 theo Jurgen Klopp chia s\u1ebb l\u00e0 \u00f4ng ch\u1eb3ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i suy ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, anh em nh\u00e0 Neville l\u1ea1i l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng nghi ng\u1edd s\u1ef1 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a Shaqiri trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i \u1edf Stoke City, khi cho r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn h\u1ebft kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng \u0111\u1ec3 ra \u0111i cho d\u1ec5.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e1p l\u1eddi, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 b\u00ecnh th\u1ea3n: &ldquo;H\u1ecd l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Man United &ndash; CLB ch\u1eb3ng \u01b0a g\u00ec Liverpool. T\u00f4i hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi y\u00eau th\u00edch, v\u00e0 c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng \u01b0a. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n t\u1ed1n th\u1eddi gian b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u00e0 t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Shaqiri kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch c\u1ee7a huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i M.U\" title=\"Liverpool mua Shaqiri t\u1eeb Stoke v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 13,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/14/shaqiri-buong-loi-dap-tra-khi-bi-huyen-thoai-mu-chui-thang-mat.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Shaqiri kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch c\u1ee7a huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i M.U</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u 3 n\u0103m t\u1ea1i Premier League v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. T\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o, t\u00f4i c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u. Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, v\u00ec v\u1eady t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 ai. M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng t\u00f4i l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hay nh\u1ea5t Stoke City m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc. L\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec c\u1ea3.&rdquo;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, sau khi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Xherdan Shaqiri kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch, anh c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi Liverpool, v\u1ec1 \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y Jurgen Klopp v\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1992 mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u danh hi\u1ec7u, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 Champions League.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-liverpool-21-man-city-icc-2018-326-192055.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/26/video-tong-hop-liverpool-21-man-city-icc-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-liverpool-21-man-city-icc-2018-326-192055.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Liverpool 2-1 Man City (ICC 2018)</span><br>\r\nS\u1ef1 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Mohamed Salah sau khi v\u00e0o s\u00e2n trong hi\u1ec7p 2 \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf th\u1eafng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea1nh tranh quen thu\u1ed9c t\u1ea1i Premier League trong tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tan-binh-liverpool-ha-muc-tieu-vo-dich-champions-league-172-192043.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/14/tan-binh-liverpool-ha-muc-tieu-vo-dich-champions-league.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tan-binh-liverpool-ha-muc-tieu-vo-dich-champions-league-172-192043.html\">T\u00e2n binh Liverpool h\u1ea1 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League</span><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Xherdan Shaqiri m\u1ea1nh d\u1ea1n h\u1ea1 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Anfield trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1649","checkdouble":"192051"},{"date":"09:41 26/07","title":"Sao M.U c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi c\u00f3 HLV m\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/26/sao-mu-cam-thay-hanh-phuc-khi-co-hlv-moi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Man United \u2013 Andreas Pereira chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Michael Carrick v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi l\u1ebd r\u1ea5t t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nPereira vui m\u1eebng khi c\u00f3 th\u1ea7y m\u1edbi<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil, Andreas Pereira \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1ea1i La Liga, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi quay v\u1ec1 Man United v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 v\u00e0 \u0111ang c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i tham gia tour du \u0111\u1ea5u. Anh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i c\u1ea3 2 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1eeba qua v\u1edbi vai tr\u00f2 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m, v\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi Jose Mourinho.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eebng xem Carrick l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n anh \u0111\u00e1ng ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 \u1edf Man United, Pereira \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u t\u1eeb ti\u1ec1n b\u1ed1i, v\u00e0 cho bi\u1ebft r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng khi Carrick tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd HLV sau khi gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7. Sao tr\u1ebb Brazil h\u1ebft l\u1eddi ca ng\u1ee3i:<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Anh \u1ea5y \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. Carrick lu\u00f4n b\u1ea3o t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m g\u00ec v\u00e0 gi\u00fap t\u00f4i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n. N\u1ebfu t\u00f4i l\u00e0m sai hay \u0111\u00fang, anh \u1ea5y c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chia s\u1ebb. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi b\u1edfi anh \u1ea5y c\u0169ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Andreas Pereira chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Michael Carrick \" title=\"Pereira\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/sao-mu-cam-thay-hanh-phuc-khi-co-hlv-moi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Andreas Pereira chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Michael Carrick&nbsp;</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n&ldquo;R\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. V\u00e0 khi anh \u1ea5y n\u00f3i v\u1edbi b\u1ea1n m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3, n\u00f3 r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp thu. T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t may m\u1eafn khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a Carrick&rdquo; &ndash; Andreas Pereira chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00e0n anh.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn ra m\u1eaft M.U v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 8/2014, \u0111\u1ebfn nay sao tr\u1ebb Brazil ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 12 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. Anh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean b\u1ecb g\u1eedi \u0111i cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n nh\u01b0ng l\u00fac n\u00e0y, \u0111\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh v\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, \u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n trong suy ngh\u0129 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd l\u00e0m t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ec3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y. T\u00f4i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u1eeb khi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u, nh\u01b0ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ch\u01a1i \u1edf b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0o mi\u1ec5n l\u00e0 HLV y\u00eau c\u1ea7u.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;L\u00fac n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 6, nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i s\u1ed1 8. T\u00f4i \u0111ang h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi t\u1eeb Carrick v\u00e0 HLV Mourinho. H\u1ecd \u0111ang gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0 t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t&rdquo; &ndash; Andreas Pereira chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Michael Carrick v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cuc-nong-mourinho-noi-dien-muon-tong-khu-martial-cang-nhanh-cang-tot-172-192038.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/14/cuc-nong-mourinho-noi-dien-muon-tong-khu-martial-cang-nhanh-cang-tot.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cuc-nong-mourinho-noi-dien-muon-tong-khu-martial-cang-nhanh-cang-tot-172-192038.html\">C\u1ef0C N\u00d3NG: Mourinho n\u1ed5i \u0111i\u00ean, mu\u1ed1n t\u1ed1ng kh\u1ee9 Martial c\u00e0ng nhanh c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t</span><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng MU b\u00e1n Anthony Martial l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao, HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111ang r\u1ea5t t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y r\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i b\u1ea3n doanh c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng b\u1ea1n g\u00e1i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00f3n c\u1eadu...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/mu-vs-ac-milan-tran-dau-icc-2018-ngay-hom-nay-372-192027.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/mu-vs-ac-milan-tran-dau-icc-2018-ngay-hom-nay.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/mu-vs-ac-milan-tran-dau-icc-2018-ngay-hom-nay-372-192027.html\">TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP MU vs AC Milan 10h00 ng\u00e0y 26/7 (ICC 2018)</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp MU vs AC Milan: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Manchester United vs AC Milan gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1648","checkdouble":"192053"},{"date":"10:50 26/07","title":"Ibrahimovic c\u00fai \u0111\u1ea7u xin l\u1ed7i NHM MU v\u00e0 l\u00fd do b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/6/10/ibrahimovic-cui-dau-xin-loi-nhm-mu-va-ly-do-bat-ngo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n nu\u1ed1i ti\u1ebfc v\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Old Trafford v\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh s\u1edbm h\u01a1n trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Zlatan Ibrahimovic t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng ngay trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Man Utd v\u1edbi 28 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n mang v\u1ec1 c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap danh hi\u1ec7u Europa League v\u00e0 League Cup.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian \u1edf Old Trafford \u0111\u1eb9p \u0111\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng ng\u1eafn ng\u1ee7i bi\u1ebft bao khi v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 bu\u1ed9c l\u00f2ng ph\u1ea3i ra \u0111i \u1edf n\u0103m th\u1ee9 hai trong s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">H\u01a1n th\u1ebf n\u1eefa \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 35-36 x\u1ebf b\u00f3ng s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta c\u0169ng kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n n\u1eefa \u1edf Zlatan, khi \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p d\u00f9 c\u00f3 c\u00f2n v\u1eb9n nguy\u00ean c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u1ecfa l\u1ea5p y\u1ebfu \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a anh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ibra xin l\u1ed7i MU v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 s\u1edbm h\u01a1n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ibra xin l\u1ed7i MU v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 s\u1edbm h\u01a1n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/6/10/ibrahimovic-cui-dau-xin-loi-nhm-mu-va-ly-do-bat-ngo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ibra xin l\u1ed7i MU v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 s\u1edbm h\u01a1n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u0169ng ch\u00ednh v\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y l\u1ea1i c\u00e0ng khi\u1ebfn Ibra c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ed1i h\u1eadn nh\u01b0 Robin Van Persie thu\u1edf n\u00e0o, r\u1eb1ng anh \u0111\u00e3 \u201cv\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 h\u01a1i mu\u1ed9n\u201d. L\u1eddi xin l\u1ed7i ch\u00e2n th\u00e0nh v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 th\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m ph\u1ea7n ki\u00eau h\u00e3nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u00f4i sao B\u1eafc \u00c2u g\u1eedi t\u1edbi c\u00e1c C\u0110V Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i xin l\u1ed7i v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1ea5y l\u00e0m ti\u1ebfc cho fan Man Utd. N\u1ebfu h\u1ecd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y t\u00f4i s\u1edbm h\u01a1n v\u00e0 tr\u1ebb h\u01a1n, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t con s\u01b0 t\u1eed r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c.\u201d - Ibra xin l\u1ed7i MU<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, Premier League s\u1ebd b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t trong m\u1ed1i nguy l\u1edbn h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u, khi t\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u0103n t\u01b0\u01a1i nu\u1ed1t s\u1ed1ng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y v\u00e0o b\u1eefa s\u00e1ng thay v\u00ec d\u00f9ng cho bu\u1ed5i tr\u01b0a. D\u00f9 sao th\u00ec t\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00e0 chinh ph\u1ee5c n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh r\u1ed3i. H\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n t\u00f4i, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng v\u00e0 ra \u0111i.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f2n c\u1ea7n th\u00eam r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 chia s\u1ebb c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, nh\u01b0ng h\u00e3y c\u1ee9 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi c\u1ea3m \u01a1n bao la \u0111i. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n d\u00e0nh n\u00f3 cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng ai li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn Man Utd, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t c\u00e1c C\u0110V, v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m cho t\u00f4i. Hy v\u1ecdng h\u1ecd c\u0169ng s\u1ebd h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac nh\u01b0 t\u00f4i.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 l\u00e2u nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 cho m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 khi ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1c nhau, may m\u1eafn h\u01a1n n\u1eefa v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 h\u1ebft l\u00f2ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3, gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 C\u0110V.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cMan Utd s\u1ebd m\u00e3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u1ea3nh gh\u00e9p \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t n\u1ee5 c\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u00ean m\u00f4i. Ch\u00fac cho CLB m\u1ecdi s\u1ef1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1647","checkdouble":"192054"}]}
